A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-population-birthrate-hospitals-give-up-delivering-babies-obstetrics-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710919473000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fa4b4b2417f97b87cd87f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-population-birthrate-hospitals-give-up-delivering-babies-obstetrics-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22China%20has%20been%20stepping%20up%20measures%20to%20encourage%20marriage%20and%20parenthood.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22htan%40insider.com%20(Huileng%20Tan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-population-birthrate-hospitals-give-up-delivering-babies-obstetrics-2024-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHe%20Said%20Bhabhi%2C%20I%20Need%20Money.%20Then%20He%20Killed%20My%20Sons%2C%26quot%3B%20Recounts%20UP%20Woman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHours%20after%20her%20two%20sons%2C%206%20and%2011%2C%20were%20brutally%20murdered%2C%20allegedly%20by%20a%20man%20the%20family%20knew%20well%2C%20a%20mother%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Budaun%20is%20asking%20one%20question%20repeatedly%20-%20Why%3F%20Sangita%2C%20the%20mother%20of%20Ayush%20and%20Ahaan%2C%20recounted%20to%20NDTV%20the%20events%20leading%20to%20the%20crime%20that%20has%20shocked%20the%20neighbourhood.%20The%20accused%2C%20Sajid%2C%20ran%20a%20barber%20shop%20near%20the%20family's%20two-storey%20house.%20He%20was%20later%20shot%20dead%20in%20an%20encounter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%206%20pm%20yesterday%2C%20Sajid%20shut%20his%20shop%20and%20came%20over.%20He%20asked%20for%20a%20hair%20clip%20for%20women.%20Sangita%2C%20who%20ran%20a%20beauty%20parlour%2C%20gave%20him%20one.%20Then%20he%20told%20me%2C%20'Bhabhi%2C%20I%20need%20Rs%205%2C000'.%20I%20called%20my%20husband%20and%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20give%20him%20the%20money.%20I%20gave%20him%20Rs%205%2C000.%20He%20said%20he%20needed%20money%20because%20his%20wife%20is%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20is%20due%20for%20delivery%20at%2011%20pm%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20then%20said%20he%20is%20anxious%20and%20the%20wait%20seems%20long.%20I%20said%20it%20will%20pass.%20I%20gave%20him%20a%20cup%20of%20tea%20and%20he%20went%20upstairs%20with%20my%20eldest%20son%20(Ayush).%20There%20he%20killed%20my%20sons.%20My%20seven-year-old%20son%20ran%20downstairs.%20Even%20he%20had%20been%20attacked%20and%20his%20hand%20was%20bleeding.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20killed%20too%2C%20but%20he%20escaped%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20has%20told%20police%20that%20Sajid%20fled%20with%20his%20brother%20Javed%2C%20who%20was%20waiting%20outside.%20The%20police%20have%20said%20that%20when%20they%20caught%20up%20with%20Sajid%2C%20he%20fired%20at%20them%20and%20was%20shot%20dead%20in%20retaliatory%20firing.%20Javed%20is%20still%20on%20the%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20and%20there%20is%20no%20clarity%20yet%20on%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20crime.%20The%20family%20has%20denied%20reports%20that%20there%20was%20a%20dispute%20between%20the%20children's%20father%20Vinod%20and%20Sajid.%20However%2C%20Vinod%20has%20denied%20any%20dispute.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20dispute%20with%20him.%20I%20was%20away%20for%20work%20when%20he%20came%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20has%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20could%20be%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20crime%2C%20Sangita%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20no%20enmity%20with%20anybody%2C%20I%20do%20not%20know%20if%20someone%20else%20is%20behind%20this.%20Javed%20should%20be%20questioned%20in%20front%20of%20us.%20He%20should%20be%20asked%20why%20they%20did%20this.%20Did%20someone%20else%20put%20them%20to%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBareilly%20police%20chief%20Dr%20Rakesh%20Kumar%20Singh%20said%20they%20are%20investigating%20the%20motive%20be