0issued%20a%20challan%20of%20Rs%202%2C000%20and%20asked%20to%20remove%20the%20back%20portion%20of%20the%20car.%20I%20have%20invested%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20in%20this%20car%20and%20worked%20day%20and%20night%20to%20make%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20said%20that%20his%20'rath'%20(chariot)%20was%20intended%20to%20be%20used%20only%20during%20the%20wedding%20season%20and%20will%20not%20ply%20on%20the%20roads%20otherwise.%20He%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20similar%20vehicles%20were%20operating%20in%20other%20regions%20such%20as%20Bihar%20and%20Pratapgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20his%20creation%20now%20parked%20outside%20a%20police%20station%20in%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%20and%20uploaded%20on%20social%20media%20has%20attracted%20a%20lot%20of%20comments%20from%20users.%20The%20video%20shows%20a%20crowd%20of%20onlookers%20and%20a%20few%20policemen%20standing%20around%20the%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20cited%20safety%20concerns%20as%20the%20primary%20reason%20for%20confiscating%20the%20vehicle.%20The%20police%20said%20the%20car%20was%20modified%20without%20proper%20authorization%20under%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYesterday%2C%20a%20modified%20car%20was%20seized.%20Due%20to%20the%20enforcement%20of%20the%20the%20Model%20code%20of%20Conduct%2C%20police%20have%20been%20conducting%20vehicle%20checks%20and%20this%20modified%20car%20was%20intercepted%20by%20traffic%20police%20during%20one%20such%20inspection.%20Modifications%20require%20permission%20from%20the%20RTO%20department%2C%20and%20the%20vehicle%20was%20seized%20under%20Section%20207%20of%20the%20Motor%20Vehicles%20Act.%20We%20are%20investigating%20further%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Assistant%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%20Vishal%20Pandey.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2F