tions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneous%20elections%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20assembly%20will%20be%20held%20in%20four%20states%3A%20Sikkim%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3Cbr%3E%5CnJammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20under%20President's%20Rule%20since%202018%2C%20will%20not%20have%20simultaneous%20elections%20due%20to%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy-elections%20will%20also%20be%20conducted%20for%2026%20assembly%20seats%20across%20multiple%20states%2C%20including%20Bihar%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Jharkhand%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20and%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EElection%20Commission's%20Measures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20has%20taken%20several%20measures%20to%20ensure%20fair%20and%20transparent%20elections.%20Special%20attention%20is%20given%20to%20combatting%20fake%20news%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20severe%20penalties%20for%20dissemination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrict%20guidelines%20are%20in%20place%20to%20prevent%20hate%20speeches%20and%20maintain%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20electoral%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecial%20provisions%20are%20made%20for%20elderly%20voters%20above%20the%20age%20of%2085%20and%20persons%20with%20disabilities%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20vote%20from%20home.%3Cbr%3E%5CnApproximately%2082%20lakh%20voters%20fall%20under%20the%20category%20of%20those%20above%20the%20age%20of%2085.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710913200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-11%2Fmpbfnv4_election-generic-afp650_625x300_02_November_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnomination-process-begins-for-lok-sabha-elections-after-poll-body-notice-5273860%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20nomination%20process%20for%20102%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20across%2021%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20for%20the%202024%20general%20elections%20with%2