t%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdespite-mcc-pune-railway-station-has-posters-of-pm-modi-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delta%20Pilot%20Gets%2010%20Months%20in%20Jail%20After%20Trying%20To%20Fly%20Plane%20While%20Drunk%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20drunk%20pilot%20who%20tried%20to%20fly%20a%20Delta%20Airlines%20plane%20from%20Scotland%20to%20the%20US%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20jail%20for%2010%20months.%20According%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbusiness%2F2024%2Fmar%2F19%2Fpilot-who-tried-to-fly-plane-from-edinburgh-to-new-york-while-drunk-is-jailed%5C%22%3EGuardian%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Captain%20Lawrence%20Russell%2C%2063%2C%20was%20found%20to%20be%20almost%20two-and-a-half%20times%20over%20the%20alcohol%20blood%20limit%20on%20the%20day%20he%20was%20due%20to%20pilot%20the%20Boeing%20767%20plane%20from%20Edinburgh%20to%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20happened%20on%20June%2016%20last%20year%20when%20Mr%20Russell%20arrived%20at%20baggage%20control%2080%20minutes%20before%20departure%20wearing%20his%20pilot's%20uniform.%20However%2C%20his%20carry-on%20luggage%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20X-ray%20scanner%20when%20it%20was%20found%20to%20contain%20two%20bottles%20of%20Jagermeister%2C%C2%A0one%20of%20which%20was%20opened%20and%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20under%20half%20full.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20failed%20a%20breath%20test%20and%20his%20blood%20sample%20showed%20he%20had%2049%20milligrams%20of%20alcohol%20in%20100%20millilitres%20of%20blood%20-%20the%20legal%20limit%20being%2020mg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Csection%20data-component%3D%5C%22text-block%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2063-year-old%20was%20sentenced%20at%20an%20Edinburgh%20court%20after%20pleading%20guilty%20to%20reporting%20for%20duty%20as%20a%20pilot%20while%20being%20impaired%20through%20alcohol.%20Sheriff%20Alison%20Stirling%20said%20a%20prison%20sente