BC.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20existing%20treatments%20suppress%20HIV%2C%20they%20can't%20eliminate%20it%20entirely.%20This%20new%20research%2C%20though%20in%20its%20early%20stages%2C%20offers%20hope%20for%20a%20complete%20eradication%20of%20the%20virus%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fhealth-68609297%5C%22%3Ethe%20news%20outlet.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20University%20of%20Amsterdam%20team%20presented%20their%20findings%20as%20a%20summary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eccmid.org%2F%5C%22%3Eat%20a%20medical%20conference.%3C%2Fa%3E%20They%20emphasise%20that%20this%20is%20a%20preliminary%20concept%20and%20won't%20translate%20to%20a%20cure%20immediately.%20Further%20research%20is%20needed%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20effectiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20like%20Dr%20James%20Dixon%2C%20Associate%20Professor%20of%20Stem%20Cell%20and%20Gene%20Therapy%20Technologies%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Nottingham%2C%20agree%20that%20a%20full%20evaluation%20of%20the%20research%20is%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20interesting%20study%20in%20which%20gene-editing%20technology%20has%20been%20used%20to%20remove%20the%20permanent%20nature%20of%20how%20HIV%20inserts%20and%20retains%20its%20genome%20in%20that%20of%20patient%20cells.%20Much%20more%20work%20will%20be%20needed%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20results%20of%20these%20cell%20assays%20can%20happen%20in%20the%20entire%20body%20for%20future%20therapies.%20As%20this%20is%20not%20peer%20reviewed%2C%20it%20will%20be%20important%20to%20assess%20the%20specific%20data%20that%20confirms%20the%20findings%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20much%20more%20development%20needed%20before%20this%20could%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20those%20with%20HIV%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencemediacentre.org%2Fexpert-reaction-to-conference-abstract-about-eliminating-hiv-in-cell-culture-using-crispr-cas-gene-editing-technology%2