t%3B.%20She%20noted%20that%20malnutrition%20had%20been%20basically%20%26quot%3Bnon-existant%26quot%3B%20in%20Gaza%20before%20the%20war.%20United%20Nations%20human%20rights%20chief%20Volker%20Turk%20denounced%20the%20rampant%20hunger%20and%20looming%20famine%20in%20Gaza.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-may-be-using-starvation-as-weapon-of-war-un%2Farticleshow%2F108635849.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-may-be-using-starvation-as-weapon-of-war-un%2Famp_articleshow%2F108635849.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-may-be-using-starvation-as-weapon-of-war-un%2Famp_articleshow%2F108635849.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%223%20Seats%20For%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda's%20Party%20As%20BJP%20Seals%20Karnataka%20Seat%20Deal%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20clock%20ticking%20for%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20sealed%20the%20seat-sharing%20deal%20with%20the%20Janata%20Dal%20(Secular)%20in%20Karnataka.%20The%20HD%20Deve%20Gowda-led%20party%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20has%20managed%20to%20secure%20three%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20seat-sharing%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JDS%20will%20be%20contesting%20Karnataka's%20Mandya%2C%20Hassan%20and%20Kolar%20seats%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20Also%2C%20in%20Bangalore%20Rural%2C%20Mr%20Deve%20Gowda's%20son-in-law%20CN%20Manjunath%20will%20contest%20on%20the%20BJP's%20lotus%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20days%20after%20JDS%20leaders%20expressed%20their%20concerns%20to%20the%20party%20leadership%20after%20the%20BJP%20announced%20candidates%20for%2020%20out%20of%20the%20state's%2028%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20their%20meeting%20with%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Deve%20Gowda%20and%20his%20son%20and%20senior%20JDS%20leader%20HD%20Kumaraswamy%2C%20the%20leaders%20said%20that%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20were%20not%20taking%20them%20into%20confidence%20in%20their%20planning%20for%20the%20upcoming%20election.%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20they%20said%2C%20were%20not%20calling%20them%20to%20any%20meeting%20and%20that%20this%20was%20harmful%20for%20the%20party.%20Mr%20Kumaraswamy%20had%20then%20declared%20that%20the%20JDS%20will%20announce%20candidates%20on%20its%20own%20if%20they%20did%20not%20get%20three%20seats%20as%20part%20of%20the%20seat-sharing%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%2025%20out%20of%20the%20state's%2028%20seats%2C%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20JDS%20winning%20one%20each.%20Currently%2C%20the%20Congress%20is%20in%20power%20in%20the%20southern%20state%20after%20its%20thumping%20state%20polls%20win%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20three%20seats%20the%20JDS%20has%20secured%2C%20Kolar%20is%20currently%20held%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20Hassan%20by%20the%20JDS%20and%20Mandya%20by%20an%20Independent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seat-sharing%20talks%20between%20the%20JDS%20and%20BJP%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20had%20hit%20an%20impasse%20over%20the%20Kolar%20seat.%20The%20BJP%20wanted%20to%20hold%20on%20to%20the%20seat%20because%20they%20won%20it%20last%20time%2C%20but%20the%20JDS%20had%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20will%20not%20settle%20for%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20deadlock%2C%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20had%20taken%20a%20swipe%2C%20with%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar%20saying%20that%20the%20JDS%20is%20%26quot%3Bembarrassed%20by%20its%20alliance%20with%20BJP%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20regional%20party%20does%20not%20need%20an%20alliance%20to%20contest%20two%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710910800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fd