B%20Zomato%20CEO%20Deepinder%20Goyal%20tweeted%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUpdate%20on%20our%20pure%20veg%20fleet%20%E2%80%94%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20we%20are%20going%20to%20continue%20to%20have%20a%20fleet%20for%20vegetarians%2C%20we%20have%20decided%20to%20remove%20the%20on-ground%20segregation%20of%20this%20fleet%20on%20the%20ground%20using%20the%20colour%20green.%20All%20our%20riders%20%E2%80%94%20both%20our%20regular%20fleet%2C%20and%20our%20fleet%20for%20vegetarians%2C%20will%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Deepinder%20Goyal%20(%40deepigoyal)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdeepigoyal%2Fstatus%2F1770290326810280128%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2020%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20explained%20that%20customers%20who%20opt%20for%20the%20'pure%20veg'%20option%20can%20see%20on%20the%20mobile%20app%20that%20their%20orders%20are%20being%20delivered%20by%20the%20'veg%20only'%20fleet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20ensure%20that%20our%20red%20uniform%20delivery%20partners%20are%20not%20incorrectly%20associated%20with%20non-veg%20food%2C%20and%20blocked%20by%20any%20RWAs%20or%20societies%20during%20any%20special%20days...%20our%20rider's%20physical%20safety%20is%20of%20paramount%20importance%20to%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20now%20realise%20that%20even%20some%20of%20our%20customers%20could%20get%20into%20trouble%20with%20their%20landlords%2C%20and%20that%20would%20not%20be%20a%20nice%20thing%20if%20that%20happened%20because%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Goyal%20said%20in%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20thanked%20the%20social%20media%20for%20raising%20these%20points%20following%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bpure%20veg%26quot%3B%20service%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20made%20us%20understand%20the%20unintended%20consequences%20of%20this%20rollout.%20All%20the%20love%2C%20and%20all%20the%20brickbats%20were%20all%20so%20useful%20-%20and%20helped%20us%20get%20to%20this%20optimal%20point.%20We%20are%20always%20listening%2C%20without%20unnecessary%20ego%2C%20or%20pride.%20We%20look%20forward%20to%20continue%20serving%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bpure%20veg%26quot%3B%20service%20and%20the%20separate%20colour%20code%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%20on%20social%20media%20yesterday%2C%20with%20some%20users%20calling%20it%20a%20form%20of%20modern-day%20casteism.%20Others%20had%20pointed%20out%20how%20this%20may%20lead%20to%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20entry%20of%20red-uniform%20delivery%20partners%20in%20apartment%20complexes%20where%20vegetarians%20are%20in%20a%20majority.%20This%2C%20they%20said%2C%20would%20lead%20to%20inconvenience%20for%20those%20ordering%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20Some%20users%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20this%20may%20lead%20to%20problems%20for%20tenants%20ordering%20non-vegetarian%20food%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20localities%20where%20it%20is%20frowned%20upon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20had%20yesterday%20said%20they%20had%20decided%20to%20introduce%20the%20%26quot%3Bpure%20veg%26quot%3B%20service%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20feedback%20from%20customers.%20%26quot%3BIndia%20has%20the%20largest%20percentage%20of%20vegetarians%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20feedback%20we've%20gotten%20from%20them%20is%20that%20they%20are%20very%20particular%20about%20how%20their%20food%20is%20cooked%2C%20and%20how%20their%20food%20is%20handled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%20He%20had%20said%20that%20for%20this%20service%2C%20Zomato%20will%20rope%20in%20restaurants%20serving%20only%20vegetarian%20food%20and%20the%20delivery%20partners%20in%20this%20service%20will%20not%20handle%20any%20non-vegetarian%20packets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20why%20did%20we%20need%20to%20separate%20the%20fleets%3F%20Because%20despite%20everyone's%20best%20efforts%2C%20sometimes%20the%20food%20spills%20into%20the%20delivery%20boxes.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20the%20smell%20of%20the%20previous%20order%20travels%20to%20the%20next%20order%2C%20and%20may%20lead%20to%20the%20next%20order%20smelling%20of%20the%20previous%20order.%20For%20this%20reason%2C%20we%20had%20to%20separate%20the%20fleet%20for%20veg%20orders%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Zomato%20CEO%20explained.%20He%20stressed%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bpure%20veg%26quot%3B%20service%20strictly%20serves%20a%20dietary%20preference%2C%20irrespective%20of%20a%20person's%20religion%20or%20caste.%20Mr%20Goyal%20had%2C%20however%2C%20said%20they%20will%20%26quot%3Broll%20back%26quot%3B%20the%20service%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20heartbeat%26quot%3B%20if%20there%20are%20negative%20social%20repercussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20understand%20our%20social%20responsibility%20due%20to%20this%20change%2C%20and%20we%20will%20not%20back%20down%20from%20solving%20it%20when%20the%20need%20arises.%20Please%20note%20that%20this%20Pure%20Veg%20Mode%2C%20or%20the%20Pure%20Veg%20Fleet%20doesn't%20serve%20or%20alienate%20any%20religious%2C%20or%20political%20preference%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710910740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv98lubqo_zomato-dresses_625x300_20_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fzomato-rolls-back-green-uniform-for-veg-fleet-all-riders-to-wear-red-5273211%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20an%20outcry%20over%20its%20announcement%20of%20a%20'pure%20veg'%20fleet%2C%20Zomato%20has%20said%20all%20its%20delivery%20partners%20will%20continue%20to%20wear%20red%2C%20rolling%20back%20its%20decision%20to%20introduce%20a%20green%20uniform%20for%20those%20delivering%20food%20to%20vegetarians%20under%20the%20new%20service.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%2