%20Muslim%20student%20leader%20of%20Bodoland%20was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F845767%2Fall-india-bodoland-minority-students-union-president-shot-dead-organisation-calls-indefinite-strike%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F845767%2Fall-india-bodoland-minority-students-union-president-shot-dead-organisation-calls-indefinite-strike%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710991665044000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw23qTzbKbAx13zYH6tw3lec%5C%22%3Eshot%20dead%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20broad%20daylight%20in%20Kokrajhar%2C%20and%20no%20justice%20is%20delivered%20till%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourteen-year-old%20Noor%20Nehar%20Khatoon%20died%20by%20suicide%20after%20not%20finding%20her%20name%20in%20the%20Assam%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20list%20of%20physical%20violence%20is%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuslims%20are%20vilified%20and%20dehumanised%20regularly%20in%20society.%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20population%20is%20about%2034%25%20Muslims.%20They%20are%20seen%20as%20socially%20unwanted%20and%20dangerous%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cindigenous%E2%80%9D%20cultures%20of%20Assam.%20They%20have%20never%20been%20integrated%20into%20Assamese%20society%20and%20the%20state.%20Their%20recent%20exclusion%20from%20state-run%20Mission%20Basundhara%2C%20which%20was%20admitted%20by%20the%20Assam%20CM%20on%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20assembly%20to%20give%20land%20to%20the%20landless%20further%20proves%20this%20point.%20Or%20take%20the%20example%20of%20the%20Miya%20museum.%20The%20very%20thought%20of%20putting%20Miya%20cultural%20artefacts%20in%20the%20Srimanta%20Sankardev%20Kalakshetra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fwhy-the-miya-museum-in-assam-was-sealed-2-days-after-it-opened-1156796.html%5C%22%3Eappeared%20to%20be%20grossly%20insulting%20for%20the%20caste%20Assamese%20society%20and%20its%20politicians%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20shows%20how%20much%20Muslims%20are%20accepted%20in%20Assamese%20society.%20This%20distance%20has%20created%20a%20permanent%20rapture%20in%20society%20where%20they%20are%20seen%20as%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%E2%80%9D%20beings.%20The%20NRC%20legitimises%20this%20social%20desire%20of%20people%20to%20see%20them%20as%20illegal%20and%20punishes%20them%20collectively.%20The%20state%20and%20society%20both%20abandoned%20them%20long%20ago%2C%20and%20nothing%20has%20stopped%20them%20from%20wounding%20them%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20skit%20which%20shows%20a%20policeman%20punishing%20the%20two%20Muslims%20speaks%20volumes.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20one%20can%20read%20it%20as%20the%20police%20state%20in%20Assam%20being%20given%20some%20attention%2C%20but%20at%20the%20same%20time%20the%20singling%20out%20of%20the%20victim%20gives%20room%20to%20manufacture%20the%20ideal%20criminal%20%E2%80%93the%20Muslim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20sociological%20fact%20that%20crime%20is%20present%20in%20all%20societies%20and%20all%20cultures.%20To%20single%20out%20one%20community%20shows%20the%20nature%20of%20social%20outlook%20towards%20Muslims%20in%20Assam%20today.%20Census%20officer%20C.S.%20Mullan%20wrote%20the%201931%20Census%20report%20on%20Assam%20where%20he%20warned%20that%20migrant%20Muslim%20peasants%20were%20going%20to%20colonise%20Assam%20by%20occupying%20or%20bringing%20large%20swathes%20of%20land%20under%20cultivation.%20The%20trail%20of%20this%20document%20has%20found%20its%20way%20to%20the%20NRC%20and%20many%20such%20bureaucratic%20documents%20and%20citizenship-related%20deliberations%20in%20post-colonial%20Assam%20and%20is%20one%20of%20the%20primary%20sources%20that%20began%20creating%20anxiety%20among%20the%20Assamese.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20dehumanisation%20at%20the%20Bodoland%20University%20deserves%20further%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20university%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThings%20have%20been%20far%20from%20what%20is%20ideal%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.booksetgo.com%2Fproducts%2Fthe-idea-of-a-university-essays%3Fvariant%3D20213055127665%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.booksetgo.com%2Fproducts%2Fthe-idea-of-a-university-essays%3Fvariant%253D20213055127665%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710991665044000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw3NQZz3cNceQvT05Q-kVPrB%5C%22%3Esecular%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0or%20liberal%20ethos%20that%20should%20be%20part%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20university.%20Gopal%20Guru%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2020%2F2%2Feditorials%2Funiversity-idea.html%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520university%2520as%2520an%2520idea%2Cculture%2520of%2520dialogue%2520and%2520discussion.%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2020%2F2%2Feditorials%2Funiversity-idea.html%2523%3A~%3Atext%253DThe%252520university%252520as%252520an%252520idea%2Cculture%252520of%252520dialogue%252520and%252520discussion.%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710991665044000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw2MpHCue36MsHWxBSzMP1Ka%5C%22%3Eargues%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20universities%20have%20normative%20functions%20where%20they%20%E2%80%9Cinstutitutionalise%20value%20laden%20ideas%E2%80%9D%20and%20also%2C%20houses%20and%20hosts%20those%20ideas.%20Guru%20further%20notes%20that%20an%20university%20shares%20both%20social%20and%20intellectual%20commitment%2C%20along%20with%20a%20culture%20of%20dialogue%2C%20dissent%20and%20discussion.%20Apoorvanand%20has%20rightly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2020%2F14%2Fcommentary%2Fidea-university-india.html%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Indian%20universities%20are%20like%20a%20stagnant%20pond%20with%20an%20ever-expanding%20desert.%20With%20the%20mushrooming%20of%20private%20universities%2C%20public%20universities%20have%20dried%20up%2C%20and%20their%20funding%20has%20been%20further%20reduced%20and%20curtailed.%20As%20Swatahsiddha%20Sarkar%20points%20out%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2020%2F14%2Fcommentary%2Fidea-university-india.html%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.epw.in%2Fjournal%2F2020%2F14%2Fcommentary%2Fidea-university-india.html%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710991665044000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw0i6hwp6TayP_LQTkaaBV7b%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEPW%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20higher%20education%20in%20India%20has%20been%20experiencing%20massification.%20These%20shifts%20raise%20questions%20of%20justice%2C%20accessibility%2C%20equity%20and%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20university%20is%20an%20institution%20that%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20teaching%20egalitarian%20values.%20In%20India%2C%20universities%20were%20established%20to%20serve%20the%20interest%20of%20the%20colonial%20rulers.%20Universities%20exist%20to%20produce%20knowledge%20but%20also%20to%20teach.%20A%20university%20should%20draw%20faculty%20members%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%2C%20students%20and%20people%20from%20all%20communities%20should%20be%20valued%2C%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20co-existence%20must%20be%20promoted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBodoland%20University%20presents%20a%20different%20picture.%20Among%20its%2093%2B%20faculty%20members%20from%20various%20departments%2C%20not%20even%20a%20single%20university%20teacher%20is%20Muslim.%20Bodoland%20University%20runs%20two%20hostels%2C%20one%20for%20boys%20and%20another%20for%20girls.%20As%20per%20our%20sources%2C%20not%20even%20a%20single%20Muslim%20student%20stays%20in%20the%20boy%E2%80%99s%20hostel%2C%20and%20only%20one%20Muslim%20student%20stays%20in%20the%20girl%E2%80%99s%20hostel.%20This%20is%20a%20story%20of%20a%20public%20institution%20where%20about%20150%2B%20Muslim%20students%20study.%C2%A0%20The%20lack%20of%20representation%20of%20Muslims%20in%20the%20form%20of%20teachers%20has%20made%20it%20easy%20to%20stereotype%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20imperative%20to%20mention%20that%20the%20autonomous%20council%20of%20Bodoland%20Territorial%20Region%20(BTR)%20has%2040%20members%2C%20of%20which%2030%20are%20reserved%20for%20Scheduled%20Tribe%20communities.%20The%20governor%20of%20Assam%20nominates%20an%20additional%20six%20members.%20Interestingly%2C%20there%20is%20not%20even%20a%20single%20Muslim%20in%20the%20council.%20BTR%20has%20about%20a%2020%25%20Muslim%20population.%20The%20politics%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fwhither-assam-muslims-the-story-of-groups-exclusion-from-political-public-spheres%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1710991665044000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1_0bRNGMYuOZLoTOQznnXb%5C%22%3Eexclusion%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0cannot%20be%20clearer%20than%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20video%2C%20we%20can%20see%20the%20participation%20of%20hundreds%20of%20students%20in%20the%20procession.%20Though%20everyone%20was%20not%20party%20to%20this%20incident%2C%20it%20happened%20in%20front%20of%20them.%20No%20one%20was%20seen%20stopping%20them%20in%20the%20video.%20The%20presentation%20also%20became%20possible%20because%20of%20the%20many%20rehearsals%20that%20took%20place%20backstage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObviously%2C%20many%20witnessed%20the%20preparation%20of%20the%20students%20in%20question.%20Maybe%20some%20among%20them%20were%20teachers%20too.%20The%20spectacle%20of%20the%20hatred%20unfolded%20in%20broad%20daylight.%20Why%20did%20no%20one%20stop%20them%20at%20any%20stage%3F%20Did%20everyone%20think%20it%20was%20normal%3F%20Have%20we%20entered%20into%20that%20phase%20of%20society%20where%20the%20dehumanising%20of%20Muslims%20has%20become%20normal%20not%20only%20in%20societies%20but%20in%20universities%20of%20Assam%3F%20Is%20this%20a%20case%20of%20failure%20of%20education%3F%20If%20yes%2C%20whose%20failure%20is%20it%3F%20Failure%20of%20the%20teachers%3F%20The%20students%3F%20The%20administration%3F%20Who%20takes%20responsibility%20for%20such%20digressions%3F%20If%20no%20one%20apologises%20for%20such%20excess%2C%20what%20does%20it%20tell%20us%20about%20our%20society%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20a%20source%20of%20shame%20for%20the%20university.%20The%20idea%20of%20the%20university%20is%20defeated%20when%20it%20becomes%20a%20platform%20to%20perform%20hate%20and%20dehumanisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20press%20release%20dated%20March%2017%2C%202024%2C%20issued%20by%20the%20Bodoland%20University%20Student%20Union%20(BUSU)%20spoke%20about%20the%20procession.%20The%20letter%20claims%20that%20their%20intent%20was%20solely%20to%20%E2%80%9Cshed%20light%20on%20the%20prevailing%20social%20dynamics%20without%20%5Bharming%5D%20any%20particular%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wish%20to%20emphasise%20that%20there%20was%20no%20intention%20to%20marginalise%20or%20disparage%20any%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20press%20release%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20they%20are%20refusing%20to%20even%20acknowledge%20what%20they%20have%20done%20let%20alone%20express%20regret%20or%20apologise%20to%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20Bodoland%20and%20Assam.%20The%20press%20release%20is%20a%20hogwash%20and%20ironically%2C%20ends%20up%20justifying%20their%20procession%20and%20the%20manner%20of%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBodoland%20has%20witnessed%20several%20incidents%20of%20anti-Muslim%20and%20anti-Adivasi%20violence%20since%201990s.%20Most%20of%20the%20victims%20are%20yet%20to%20receive%20compensation%2C%20resettlement%20or%20rehabilitation.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20termed%20illegal%20immigrants%20and%20foreigners%20from%20Bangladesh%20by%20the%20media%20and%20politicians.%20This%20is%20usual%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Assam%20politics.%20In%20fact%2C%20many%20Muslim%20families%20could%20never%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes%20after%20facing%20violence%20and%20live%20permanently%20in%20camps.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUniversity%20spaces%20have%20been%20profoundly%20politicised%20in%20Assam%2C%20particularly%20since%20All%20Assam%20Students%E2%80%99%20Union%20(AASU)%20entered%20into%20the%20political%20sphere.%20Students%20have%20often%20been%20brought%20up%20to%20hate%20the%20%E2%80%9Cforeigner%E2%80%9D%20and%20taught%20to%20be%20political%20in%20specific%20ways%20that%20involve%20anti-foreigner%20sensibilities%20and%20aesthetics.%20Anti-minority%20sentiments%20are%20normalised%20in%20university%20spaces%20in%20Assam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20university%20should%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20teaching%20humanitarian%2C%20multicultural%2C%20democratic%20and%20egalitarian%20values%20to%20society.%20This%20is%20not%20possible%20unless%20the%20university%20recruits%20adequate%20faculty%20members%20from%20different%20communities%2C%20who%20are%20representatives%20of%20the%20social%20groups%20of%20Bodoland%2C%20especially%20the%20Muslims%20and%20other%20subaltern%20groups.%20Representation%20is%20absolutely%20central%20to%20social%20justice.%20Its%20lack%20shows%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENazimuddin%20Siddique%20teaches%20at%20Jamia%20Millia%20Islamia%20University%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20Suraj%20Gogoi%20teaches%20at%20RV%20University%2C%20Bengaluru.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710910101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20095123%2FUntitled-design-13.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwhat-a-college-skit-says-about-the-idea-of-the-university-in-assam%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20space%20such%20as%20a%20university%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20equal%20for%20everyone%20irrespective%20of%20caste%2C%20race%2C%20colour%2C%20religion%20or%20gender.%20But%20this%20is%20not