0Whose%20Vote%20Swung%20Ethics%20Decision%20Joined%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F30154328%2FSK9A9999.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Lokpal%20has%20told%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20to%20probe%20allegations%20against%20former%20Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20proceedings%20which%20have%20been%20criticised%20by%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20coram%20of%20judicial%20member%20Justice%20Abhilasha%20Kumari%20and%20members%20Archana%20Ramasundaram%20and%20Mahender%20Singh%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Flokpal-orders-cbi-probe-against-mahua-moitra%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20careful%20evaluation%20and%20consideration%20of%20the%20entire%20material%20on%20record%2C%20there%20remains%20no%20doubt%20regarding%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20allegations%20levelled%20against%20the%20RPS%2C%20most%20of%20which%20are%20supported%20by%20cogent%20evidence%2C%20are%20extremely%20serious%20in%20nature%2C%20especially%20in%20view%20of%20the%20position%20held%20by%20her.%20Therefore%2C%20in%20our%20considered%20opinion%2C%20a%20deeper%20probe%20is%20required%20to%20establish%20the%20truth%E2%80%A6%C2%A0It%20is%20a%20duty%20cast%20upon%20us%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20Act%2C%20that%20all%20attempts%20be%20made%20to%20root%20out%20corruption%20and%20corrupt%20practises%20that%20bring%20under%20their%20fold%20aspects%20such%20as%20undue%20advantage%2C%20illegal%20gain%20or%20benefit%20and%20quid%20pro%20quo%20in%20the%20discharge%20of%20public%20duties.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lokpal%20noted%20that%2C%20as%20per%20CBI%20report%20presented%20to%20them%2C%20the%20allegation%20that%20Moitra%20shared%20her%20login%20credentials%