html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEven%20MS%20Dhoni%20Made%20Blunders%20But%20Rohit%20Sharma%20Never%20Did%26quot%3B%3A%20Ex-CSK%20Star%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20cricketer%20Parthiv%20Patel%20said%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20had%20got%20the%20full%20backing%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma%20when%20they%20were%20struggling%20in%20the%20early%20part%20of%20their%20IPL%20stints%20at%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20Parthiv%20compared%20Rohit's%20leadership%20with%20CSK%20talisman%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20saying%20the%20Mumbai%20cricketer%20never%20%26quot%3Bmade%20a%20blunder%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20the%20Chennai%20captain%20had%20erred%20on%20a%20few%20occasions%20during%20his%20long%20IPL%20stint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20is%20that%20he%20(Rohit)%20supports%20his%20players.%20The%20best%20examples%20of%20this%20are%20Hardik%20Pandya%20and%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%20Bumrah%20came%20into%20the%20MI%20set%20up%20in%202014%20and%20by%202015%2C%20his%20performance%20wasn't%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Parthiv%20told%20Jio%20Cinema%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20even%20pondered%20sending%20him%20back%20after%20half%20the%20season.%20But%20Rohit%20Sharma%20believed%20in%20his%20ability%20and%20from%202016%20onwards%2C%20his%20performance%20has%20been%20excellent%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20the%20former%20India%20wicketkeeper%2C%20who%20played%2025%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%2C%20who%20came%20into%20the%20MI%20setup%20in%202014%2C%20has%20gone%20on%20to%20become%20the%20country's%20go-to%20pacer%20in%20all%20three%20formats%20and%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20Mumbai's%20success%20in%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%2C%20after%20becoming%20a%20part%20of%20the%20five-time%20champions%20in%202015%2C%20went%20on%20to%20lead%20Gujarat%20Titans%20to%20the%20IPL%20title%20in%202022%20and%20is%20now%20back%20as%20MI%20skipper%2C%20replacing%20Rohit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSame%20with%20Hardik%20Pandya.%20He%20came%20in%202015%20and%20became%20popular.%20His%202016%20season%20wasn't%20great%20but%20MI%20stuck%20with%20him%20and%20Pandya%20became%20the%20player%20he%20is%20today.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20Rohit%20brings%20a%20sense%20of%20calm%20to%20the%20side%2C%20which%20is%20unmatched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20best%20example%20is%20the%20two%20IPLs%20MI%20won%20by%20just%20one%20run%20each.%20That%20would%20not%20have%20been%20possible%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20captain%20who%20can%20stay%20calm%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20there's%20a%20tense%20match%2C%20sometimes%20wrong%20decisions%20or%20blunders%20are%20made.%20But%20the%20hallmark%20of%20Rohit%20Sharma's%20captaincy%20is%20that%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%2C%20you%20don't%20remember%20that%20he%20made%20a%20blunder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20Dhoni%20has%20made%20blunders%20like%20giving%20Pawan%20Negi%20an%20over%2C%20but%20if%20you%20see%20Rohit%2C%20you'll%20never%20see%20a%20blunder.%20Keeping%20the%20process%20simple%20is%20something%20that%20Dhoni%20advises%20but%20we%20see%20Rohit%20practice%20that%20in%20games%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Parthiv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20India%20pacer%20Zaheer%20Khan%20said%20Rohit%20takes%20decisions%20based%20on%20circumstances%2C%20which%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20tasks%20for%20a%20captain%20in%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20plan%20for%20a%20game%20in%20advance%20but%20nobody%20knows%20how%20proceedings%20will%20unfold%20in%20the%20middle.%20He%20(Rohit)%20acts%20according%20to%20situations%20and%20takes%20decisions%2C%20and%20many%20times%20they%20are%20different%20from%20what%20may%20have%20been%20planned%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that's%20his%20strength.%20In%20the%20IPL%2C%20taking%20on-the-spot%20decisions%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20challenges%20for%20captains%20and%20he%20did%20that%20well%20for%20MI%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710907620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fkoas6tf_ms-dhoni-and-rohit-sharma-bcci_625x300_19_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Feven-ms-dhoni-made-blunders-but-rohit-sharma-never-did-ex-csk-star-5268291%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parthiv%20compared%20Rohit's%20leadership%20with%20CSK%20talisman%20MS%20Dhoni%2C%20saying%20the%20Mumbai%20cricketer%20never%20%26quot%3Bmade%20a%20blunder%26quot%3B%2C%20while%20the%20Chennai%20captain%20had%20erred%20on%20a%20few%20occasions%20during%20his%20long%20IPL%20stint.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kanguva%20Teaser%3A%20It's%20Suriya%20vs%20Bobby%20Deol%20In%20A%20Dark%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAttention%20folks%2C%20the%20makers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fkanguva-new-poster-behold-the-glory-of-suriya-5267491%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EKanguva%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20dropped%20the%20teaser%20of%20the%20film%20on%20Tuesday%20evening%20and%20it%20trending%20even%20a%20day%20later.%20The%20teaser%20gives%20us%20a%20glimpse%20of%20a%20dystopian%20world%20that%20is%20engulfed%20in%20darkness.%20The%20force%20that%20can%20change%20the%20world%20is%20represented%20by%20Suriya%2C%20in%20a%20never-seen-before%20look%20what%20with%20dreadlocks%2C%20intense%20make-up.%20The%20teaser%20is%20replete%20with%20some%20high-octane%20action%20pieces%20(%20read%20sword%20fighting%2C%20dance%20around%20the%20fire%20as%20some%20chilling%20background).%20Brace%20yourselves%20for%20the%20Kanguva%20world%20-%20where%20Suriya%20is%20introd