%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fewan-mcgregor-intimacy-coordinator-sex-scenes-wife-mary-elizabeth-winstead-1235946712%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Electoral%20Bonds%20Have%20Revealed%20the%20BJP's%20Doublespeak%20on%20Corruption%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F20083549%2FGI8aa_dbEAAKTg-.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20under%20Narendra%20Modi%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%20on%20a%20slew%20of%20promises%20and%20expectations%20greatly%20constructed%20around%20his%20undertaking%20to%20eradicate%20the%20problem%20of%20corruption%20in%20India.%20It%20started%20a%20long%20tale%20involving%20Modi%20and%20corruption%20although%20paradoxically%2C%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20accusations%20have%20turned%20on%20their%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20it%20is%20time%20for%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20his%20party%20to%20be%20accused%20of%20evading%20the%20charges%20against%20the%20combine.%20If%20nothing%20else%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20entire%20leadership%20are%20guilty%20of%20not%20divulging%20information%20on%20the%20anonymous%20donations%2C%20disproportionately%20made%20to%20the%20party%20between%20March%202018%20and%20February%202023%2C%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%20pronounced%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20as%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%5C%22%3Eagainst%20the%20basic%20tenets%20of%20the%20Constitution%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20needs%20to%20be%20recalled%20that%20the%20current%20stance%20of%20the%20BJP%20stands%20in%20sharp%20contrast%20to%20its%20posture%20a%20decade%20ago.%20Coincidentally%2C%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20anti-corruption%20narrative%20for%20the%202014%20parliamentary%20elections%20was%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20century%20after%20the%201989%20elections%20saw%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%2C%20also%20a%20Congress%20prime%20minister%2C%20being%20voted%20out%20of%20office%2C%20mainly%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption%20in%20high%20places.%20In%20both%20instances%20%E2%80%93%20against%20Rajiv%E2%80%99s%20government%20and%20the%20one%20headed%20by%20Manmohan%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20investigations%20and%20insinuations%20were%20probed%20but%20came%20to%20a%20naught.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EV.P.%20Singh%20bowed%20out%20of%20office%20less%20than%20a%20year%20after%20assuming%20office%20so%20he%20had%20the%20privilege%20to%20claim%20that%20his%20successors%20were%20gentle%20with%20Rajiv%E2%80%99s%20legacy%20and%20memory%20and%20did%20not%20meticulously%20probe%20accusations.%20Modi%20has%20no%20such%20advantage%20and%20none%20of%20the%20allegations%20he%20levelled%20against%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20regime%20and%20Singh%20personally%2C%20could%20be%20proven%20by%20his%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20has%20not%20clarified%20to%20the%20people%20why%20he%20misled%20them%20by%20making%20allegations%20which%20his%20government%20has%20been%20unable%20to%20establish.%20He%20certainly%20owes%20an%20explanation%20to%20the%20people%20why%20he%20made%20false%20accusations%20which%20could%20not%20be%20substantiated%20in%20court%20and%20have%20now%20been%20given%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Watch%20%7C%20Electoral%20Bonds%3A%20CPI(M)%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Rule%20Out%20Moving%20SC%20Against%20SBI%2C%20Govt%20For%20Perjury%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fwatch-electoral-bonds-cpim-sitaram-yechury%5C%22%3EElectoral%20Bonds%3A%20CPI(M)%20Doesn%E2%80%99t%20Rule%20Out%20Moving%20SC%20Against%20SBI%2C%20Govt%20For%20Perjury%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20only%20has%20there%20been%20no%20expression%20of%20regret%2C%20but%20another%20ten%20years%20later%2C%20as%20one%20more%20parliamentary%20elections%20draw%20near%2C%20he%20continues%20on%20the%20path%20of%20first%20levelling%20charges%20and%20then%20opening%20corruption%20cases%20against%20several%20opposition%20leaders.%20He%20is%20also%20holding%20many%20of%20them%20in%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENon-disclosure%20is%20a%20common%20complaint%20made%20against%20various%20opposition%20leaders%20even%20though%20the%20BJP%20is%20showing%20no%20urgency%20to%20reveal%20all%20facts%20regarding%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20it%20received.%20These%20details%20are%20at%20the%20disposal%20of%20both%20the%20government%20and%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%20to%20continuing%20with%20past%20practice%20of%20hurling%20one%20allegation%20after%20another%20at%20adversaries%2C%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20silent%20even%20though%20they%20stand%20accused%20of%20rampant%20corruption%20by%20grabbing%20almost%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20veiled%20electoral%20funding%20tool%2C%20dubiously%20introduced%20and%20passed%20by%20the%20government%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20the%20BJP%20has%20several%20skeletons%20in%20its%20cupboard%2C%20which%20it%20is%20frantically%20trying%20to%20hide%2C%20is%20clear%20from%20stonewalling%20tactics%20whenever%20demands%20are%20made%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20reveal%20names%20of%20its%20donors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20taking%20the%20lead%2C%20which%20it%20should%20because%20it%20has%20been%20the%20ruling%20party%20for%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20besides%20also%20being%20the%20largest%20recipient%20of%20the%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20party%20spokespersons%20are%20busy%20hurling%20charges%20against%20other%20parties%20on%20a%20daily%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20necessary%20to%20recall%20some%20of%20the%20promises%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20its%20election%20manifesto%20in%202014.%20To%20begin%20with%2C%20the%20party%20asserted%20that%20other%20nations%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20with%20smaller%20size%20and%20lesser%20resources%2C%20have%20surpassed%20us%20in%20development%20parameters%E2%80%9D%20because%20of%20%E2%80%9Clack%20of%20openness%20in%20government%20and%20lack%20of%20people%E2%80%99s%20participation%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BJP%20contended%20that%20this%20resulted%20in%20%E2%80%9Cconcentration%20of%20power%20in%20a%20few%20hands%2C%20and%20lack%20of%20transparency%2C%20breeding%20corruption%20and%20nepotism%20on%20a%20massive%20scale%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFive%20elementary%20questions%20needs%20to%20be%20flagged%20at%20this%20point%3A%20One%2C%20what%20kind%20of%20transparency%20was%20ushered%20in%20the%20domain%20of%20electoral%20funding%20by%20the%20electoral%20bonds%3F%20Two%2C%20is%20it%20not%20a%20fact%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20is%20most%20centralised%20regime%20India%20has%20ever%20witnessed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%2C%20was%20not%20the%20entire%20scheme%20skewed%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BJP%20by%20opening%20the%20avenues%20for%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20come%20pouring%20into%20the%20party%20coffers%20for%20quid%20pro%20quo%20on%20part%20of%20the%20government%3F%20Four%2C%20did%20not%20the%20scheme%20allow%20money%20laundering%20in%20a%20big%20way%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20is%20the%20reluctance%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20revealing%20names%20of%20its%20donors%20an%20indication%20of%20proof%20that%20reciprocal%20decisions%20were%20taken%20and%20that%20some%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98formal%E2%80%99%20donors%20were%20not%20the%20%E2%80%98actual%E2%80%99%20ones%2C%20thereby%20suggesting%20that%20the%20standard%20practice%20of%20converting%20%E2%80%98black%E2%80%99%20into%20%E2%80%98white%E2%80%99%20and%20vice%20versa%20was%20rampant%20under%20the%20scheme%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECorruption%2C%20said%20the%20aforesaid%20manifesto%20very%20authoritatively%2C%20%E2%80%9Cis%20a%20manifestation%20of%20poor%20governance%E2%80%A6(and)%20reflects%20the%20bad%20intentions%20of%20those%20sitting%20in%20power%E2%80%9D.%20The%20BJP%20under%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20leadership%20further%20promised%20to%20usher%20in%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPublic%20awareness%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ETechnology%20enabled%20e-governance%2C%20minimising%20discretion%20in%20the%20citizen-government%20interface%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESystem-based%2C%20policy-driven%20governance%20%E2%80%93%20making%20it%20transparent.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAre%20these%20not%20golden%20words%20which%20must%20be%20shown%20to%20the%20BJP%3F%20Quite%20clearly%2C%20the%20BJP%20stands%20accused%20of%20betraying%20its%20own%20promises%20to%20the%20voters%20and%20it%20is%20up%20to%20the%20political%20adversaries%20of%20the%20party%20to%20remind%20them%20of%20this%20in%20a%20comprehensible%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Electoral%20Bonds%3A%20How%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Exposed%20Modi%20Govt's%20Double%20Standards%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-how-the-supreme-court-exposed-modi-govts-double-standards%5C%22%3EElectoral%20Bonds%3A%20How%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Exposed%20Modi%20Govt%E2%80%99s%20Double%20Standards%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3Cins%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20in%20its%20manifesto%20for%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20word%20corruption%20was%20used%20primarily%20as%20a%20malaise%20of%20the%20past%2C%20because%20by%20then%2C%20it%20was%20contended%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Ccorruption-free%20Bharat%E2%80%9D%20had%20come%20into%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20although%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20rolled%20out%20barely%20a%20year%20before%2C%20there%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20further%20electoral%20reforms%20in%202019%20(barring%20promising%20simultaneous%20elections)%20and%20how%20the%20party%20wished%20to%20additionally%20improve%20the%20vexed%20issue%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20rather%20odd%20that%20a%20major%20legislation%2C%20which%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcolumns%2Fsc-electoral-bonds-verdict-political-funding-bjp-9165672%2F%5C%22%3EBJP%20argued%3C%2Fa%3E%20revolutionised%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20funding%20by%20introducing%20an%20unprecedented%20level%20of%20transparency%20and%20accountability%E2%80%9D%2C%C2%A0should%20not%20have%20been%20flagged%20in%20its%20%E2%80%9CSankalp%20Patra%E2%80%9D%2C%20essentially%20a%20litany%20of%20what%20all%2C%20according%20to%20the%20party%2C%20were%20the%20positives%20of%20the%20government%2C%20the%20steps%20it%20had%20taken%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENo%20mention%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20was%20made%20even%20though%20the%20Congress%20promised%20to%20scrap%20the%20scheme%20if%20it%20came%20to%20power.%20Significantly%2C%20the%20tide%20had%20begun%20to%20turn%20against%20the%20instrument%20for%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Felectoral-bonds-hit-transparency-in-political-funding-says-election-commission%2Farticle26656311.ece%5C%22%3Etold%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20peak%20campaigning%20that%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%9Chit%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding%E2%80%A6contrary%20to%20government%20claims%E2%80%9D%20and%20opened%20the%20field%20for%20foreign%20corporates%20to%20%E2%80%9Cinterfere%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20the%20apex%20court%20eventually%20took%20five%20years%20since%20the%20above-mentioned%20hearing%20to%20adjudicate%20on%20the%20matter%2C%20it%20is%20now%20time%20for%20complete%20transparency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20strong%20probability%20that%20attempts%20of%20political%20parties%20to%20veil%20the%20identity%20of%20donors%20will%20fail%20in%20the%20event%20of%20the%20judiciary%20passing%20an%20order%20like%20it%20did%20for%20the%20State%20Bank%20of%20India%20which%20initially%2C%20obviously%20at%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20behest%2C%20tried%20preventing%20any%20data%20from%20being%20published%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20thereby%20prudent%20for%20every%20party%20to%20follow%20those%20who%20have%20already%20declared%20the%20nam