yGLuqq5V0w0FrB06GCgvXotz3PdnnwxrE4aloz3J7CPLu_6ldcXGmv52BoCvfAQAvD_BwE%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDallas%20to%20Denver%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Paul%20Hedrick%2C%20founder%2C%20and%20CEO%20of%20Tecovas.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F615727a000371000184319af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPaul%20Hedrick%20in%20the%20Austin%20Tecovas%20retail%20store.%3Cp%3ETecovas%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETecovas%20has%20continued%20to%20keep%20its%20handcrafted%20boots%20priced%20far%20below%20the%20high-end%20offerings%20of%20brands%20like%20Lucchese%20and%20Tony%20Lama%2C%20without%20sacrificing%20quality.%20The%20boots%20are%20all%20made%20in%20Le%C3%B3n%2C%20the%20heart%20of%20Mexico's%20renowned%20leather%20footwear%20industry%2C%20where%20artisans%20go%20through%20200%20steps%20to%20create%20Tecovas'%20boots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20Dean%20boots%20combine%20Western%20flair%20with%20rock-and-roll%20panache.%20Besides%20their%20sleek%20look%2C%20the%20boots'%20versatility%20appealed%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22First%20impressions%5C%22%3EFirst%20impressions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20wearing%20black%20Tecovas%20Dean%20boots.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F61571fc1b414c10018634fd0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20Tecovas%20boots%20are%20a%20stylish%20alternative%20to%20your%20typical%20leather%20dress%20shoe.%3Cp%3EKara%20Thurmond%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20all%20of%20Tecovas's%20boots%2C%20the%20Deans%20are%20handmade%20in%20Mexico%20using%20traditional%20methods%20and%20materials.%20This%20includes%20hand-laid%20cording%E2%80%94the%20design%20motif%20found%20on%20many%20cowboy%20boots%E2%80%94and%20Goodyear%20welting%2C%20which%20allows%20for%20easy%20resoling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dean%20boots%20are%20made%20from%20a%20buttery%20soft%20full-grain%20calfskin.%20They're%20also%20lined%20in%20leather%20and%20feature%20a%20zipper%20guard%20on%20the%20inside%20to%20prevent%20the%20metal%20from%20chafing%20your%20ankles.%20The%20Deans%20have%20slim-cut%20shafts%2C%20which%20means%20you%20don't%20need%20boot-cut%20jeans%20to%20fit%20your%20pant%20legs%20over%20them.%20They%20have%20stacked%20leather%201%201%2F4-inch%20heels%20with%20a%20rubber%20cap%20for%20traction.%20The%20boots%20are%20Goodyear%20welted%20so%20they%20can%20easily%20be%20resoled%20and%20they%20also%20have%20lemonwood%20pegging%20rather%20than%20metal%20nails.%20This%20traditional%20Western%20boot%20technique%20is%20a%20sign%20of%20great%20quality%20used%20by%20the%20best%20cowboy%20boot%20brands%2C%20since%20lemonwood%20and%20leather%20absorb%20moisture%20at%20similar%20rates%20so%20they%20will%20remain%20in%20place%20over%20the%20long%20haul.%20These%20are%20hand-hammered%20into%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20initially%20reviewed%20the%20Tecovas%20Dean%20boots%2C%20more%20colors%20and%20leather%20choices%20have%20been%20added%20to%20the%20line.%20Besides%20the%20Bourbon%2C%20a%20rich%20brown%3B%20and%20Midnight%2C%20a%20stunning%20black%20(both%20in%20a%20supple%20calfskin)%2C%20there%20are%20now%20three%20more%3A%20the%20Cafe%2C%20a%20chocolate-brown%2C%20the%20Scotch%2C%20a%20reddish%20brown%2C%20and%20Sand%2C%20an%20earthy%20beige.%20All%20three%20are%20made%20of%20goatskin%2C%20which%20is%20soft%20with%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20flexibility%2C%20yet%20still%20incredibly%20durable.%20My%20Dean%20boots%20fit%20true%20to%20size%20and%20broke%20in%20easily.%20By%20my%20second%20wear%2C%20they%20were%20comfortable%20enough%20for%20a%20four-mile%20stroll%20through%20the%20city.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20unboxed%2C%20the%20Dean%20boots%20had%20that%20rich%2C%20distinctive%20leather%20smell.%20There%20was%20no%20weird%20chemical%20odor%20or%20the%20scent%20of%20glue%20that%20you%20sometimes%20find%20with%20cheaply%20made%20boots.%20The%20zippers%20are%20solid%20and%20zip%20up%20smoothly.%20The%20workmanship%20is%20impressive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dean%20Zipper%20boots%20are%20very%20versatile%20style-wise.%20I've%20paired%20them%20with%20suits%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-t-shirt-men%5C%22%3ET-shirts%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-mens-leather-jacket%5C%22%3Eleather%20jackets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-jeans-men%5C%22%3Ejeans%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20equal%20ease.%20About%20the%20only%20thing%20I%20haven't%20tried%20them%20with%20is%20shorts%2C%20which%20is%20a%20look%20that's%20nearly%20impossible%20to%20pull%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Update%20after%202%20years%20of%20wear%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EUpdate%20after%202%20years%20of%20wear%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222761%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20pair%20of%20black%20Tecovas%20Dean%20boots%20sitting%20outside%20on%20some%20steps.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653c07980487ff031cb0dbb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222071%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20leather%20of%20my%20Tecovas%20Dean%20boots%20has%20only%20gotten%20better%20over%20time.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Amelinckx%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20in%2C%20the%20Tecovas%20Dean%20boots%20have%20conformed%20to%20my%20feet%20for%20a%20fit%20that%20feels%20like%20they%20were%20made%20just%20for%20me.%20The%20uppers%20have%20only%20gotten%20more%20handsome.%20The%20calfskin%20is%20still%20soft%20and%20supple%20and%20has%20aged%20gracefully.%20The%20hand%20laid%20decorative%20cording%20remains