kmanship%2C%20timeless%20style%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20pair%20well%20with%20pretty%20much%20any%20look%20makes%20the%20Tecovas%20Dean%20boot%20a%20real%20standout%20and%20well%20worth%20the%20investment.%20They%20cost%20%24285%20(they've%20gone%20up%20in%20price%20%2430%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20which%20is%20a%20more%20than%20reasonable%20increase%20given%20the%20state%20of%20things).%20Compared%20to%20other%20Western%20boot%20brands%20like%20Lucchese%20or%20Frye%2C%20you're%20unlikely%20to%20find%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-mens-leather-dress-boots-under-500%5C%22%3Ebetter%20men's%20leather%20dress%20boot%20under%20%24500%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20continue%20to%20highly%20recommend%20Tecovas%2C%20and%20especially%20the%20Dean%20boots%2C%20for%20both%20cowboy%20boot%20connoisseurs%20and%20newbies%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Ftecovas-dean-boots-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710887497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F615722ec00371000184317f5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Ftecovas-dean-boots-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tecovas%20makes%20affordable%2C%20stylish%20leather%20cowboy%20boots%20that%20last.%20In%20our%20Tecovas%20boots%20review%2C%20we%20detail%20how%20two%20years%20later%20they've%20held%20up%20beautifully.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Andrew%20Amelinckx)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Ftecovas-dean-boots-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Blow%E2%80%99%20Actor%20Lola%20Glaudini%20Says%20Johnny%20Depp%20Berated%20Her%20on%20Set%20and%20Called%20Her%20a%20%E2%80%98F%E2%80%94ing