20users%20on%20Threads%20can%20share%20text-based%20posts%20of%20up%20to%20500%20characters%2C%20videos%20of%20up%20to%20five%20minutes%2C%20and%20links%20and%20photos.%20Users%20can%20follow%20creators%20and%20other%20users%2C%20and%20discuss%20topics%20of%20shared%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrending%20topics%20is%20another%20addition%20that%20makes%20Threads%20and%20X%20similar%2C%20although%20other%20sites%20like%20LinkedIn%20and%20TikTok%20have%20their%20own%20version%20of%20the%20feature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrending%20on%20Threads%20is%20also%20less%20exhaustive%20than%20X.%20It's%20only%20available%20under%20the%20search%20bar%20and%20shows%20five%20topics.%20Meanwhile%2C%20X%20has%20up%20to%2030%20trending%20topics%20listed%20and%20has%20a%20section%20dedicated%20to%20it%20under%20the%20explore%20tab.%20It%20also%20shows%20up%20on%20the%20sidebar%20of%20a%20desktop.%20Threads'%20version%20is%20more%20discrete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20move%20brings%20the%20feature%20set%20of%20the%20rival%20apps%20closer%20together%2C%20Instagram%20boss%20Adam%20Mosseri%20previously%20said%20in%20a%20Threads%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2F%40mosseri%2Fpost%2FCuZ3LjhNl0m%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20company's%20goal%20%26quot%3Bisn't%20to%20replace%20Twitter%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20become%20a%20discussion%20forum%20for%20many%20users%20interested%20in%20hard%20news%20and%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthreads-never-replace-twitter-meta-zuckerberg-musk-advertisers-brands-influencers-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERather%2C%20Mosseri%20said%20it's%20creating%20a%20space%20for%20communities%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20never%20flocked%20to%20X%2C%20like%20sports%2C%20music%2C%20fashion%2C%20beauty%2C%20and%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIronically%2C%20if%20you%20took%20a%20look%20at%20the%20trending%20topics%20on%20Threads%20on%20T