artwright%20said%20it%20was%20actually%20a%20lack%20of%20sex%20that%20led%20her%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20together%20nine%20years%2C%20and%20people%20stop%20appreciating%20and%20take%20you%20for%20granted%20after%20some%20time%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that%20should%20never%20happen%20in%20a%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20Cartwright%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpagesix.com%2F2024%2F03%2F15%2Fentertainment%2Fbrittany-cartwright-lack-of-sex-led-to-jax-taylor-separation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPage%20Six%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20%26quot%3BThe%20Valley%26quot%3B%20premiere%20party%20Thursday%2C%20which%20took%20place%20at%20the%20former%20couple's%20bar%2C%20Jax's%20Studio%20City%20in%20Los%20Angeles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECartwright%20said%20that%20she's%20trying%20to%20get%20that%20physical%20intimacy%20back.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20if%20it%20doesn't%20come%20back%2C%20then%20we%20won't%20get%20back%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20told%20Page%20Six%20that%20she'd%20asked%20her%20estranged%20husband%20to%20do%20%26quot%3Bfour%20little%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20go%20to%20therapy%2C%20but%20he%20%26quot%3Bhasn't%20done%20that%20yet.%26quot%3B%20They%20also%20disagreed%20over%20whether%20to%20have%20a%20second%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20see%20if%20he%20does%20it%20all%2C%20but%20we'll%20also%20see%20if%20it%20changes%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECartwright%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fbrittany-cartwright-says-she-and-jax-taylor-had-a-horrible-fight-day-she-moved-into-airbnb-exclusive-8609746%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeople%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20same%20event%20that%20she%20and%20Taylor%20had%20%26quot%3Ba%20horrible%20fight%26quot%3B%20the%20day%20she%20finally%20moved%20out%20of%20their%20shared%20home%20and%20into%20an%20Airbnb.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20packed%20up%20my%20stuff%20and%20left%2C%26quot%3B%20Cartwright%20