es-fall-3-3-124031901177_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faditya-birla-sun-life-amc-promoters-sell-11-5-stake-shares-fall-3-3-124031901177_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Faditya-birla-sun-life-amc-promoters-sell-11-5-stake-shares-fall-3-3-124031901177_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22RSS's%20%E2%80%98Anarchist%E2%80%99%20Remark%20on%20Farmers'%20Protest%20a%20Conspiracy%20to%20Defame%20Us%2C%20Farmer%20Leaders%20Say%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15203146%2Fimage-1833.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20unions%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%20have%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20ever%20since%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20annual%20report%20for%202023-24%20claimed%20that%20the%20latest%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20was%20being%20used%20to%20restart%20anarchy%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20country%20and%20that%20separatist%20terrorism%20in%20Punjab%20has%20again%20raised%20its%20ugly%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20days%20after%20the%20said%20report%20was%20released%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20the%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(Non-political)%20and%20the%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20%E2%80%93%20farmers%E2%80%99%20bodies%20leading%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20agitation%20currently%20stuck%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20%E2%80%93%20slammed%20the%20RSS%20in%20a%20media%20briefing%20here%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20said%20that%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20assessment%20was%20not%20just%20hollow%20but%20also%20smelled%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20defame%20their%20peaceful%20agitation%20so%20that%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20question%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20remarks%20were%20uncalled%20for%20and%20alleged%20that%20it%20was%20an%20organisation%20that%20continues%20to%20promote%20polarisation%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaying%20that%20the%20comments%20in%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99%20report%20were%20unfortunate%2C%20Jagjit%20Dallewal%2C%20who%20is%20convener%20of%20the%20SKM%20(non-political)%2C%20stated%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20being%20called%20anarchists%2C%20but%20it%20was%20our%20youth%20who%20were%20attacked%20mercilessly%20by%20the%20security%20forces%20of%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana%20to%20halt%20our%20peaceful%20march%20to%20Delhi%20for%20our%20legitimate%20demands.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protesting%20farmers%E2%80%99%20demands%20include%20minimum%20support%20prices%20(MSPs)%20for%20their%20crops%2C%20debt%20waivers%20and%20pensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20said%20that%20though%20a%20young%20farmer%20was%20killed%20and%20hundreds%20more%20were%20injured%2C%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20did%20not%20retaliate%20and%20remained%20patient.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIs%20it%20anarchy%20when%20even%20today%2C%20hundreds%20of%20our%20farmers%20are%20peacefully%20waiting%20at%20the%20Punjab-Haryana%20borders%20for%20routes%20to%20Delhi%20to%20reopen%3F%E2%80%9D%2C%20Dallewal%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20it%20is%20the%20RSS%20that%20was%20causing%20anarchy%20in%20the%20country%20and%20said%20it%20tended%20to%20forget%20what%20Punjab%20stands%20for%20as%20far%20as%20sacrifice%20and%20national%20unity%20are%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20said%20that%20up%20to%20half%20of%20those%20who%20sacrificed%C2%A0their%20lives%20to%20make%20India%20free%20from%20British%20rule%20were%20from%20the%20undivided%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20look%20at%20the%20history%20of%20the%20RSS%2C%20he%20said%2C%20claiming%20that%20while%20their%20leader%20V.D.%20Savarkar%20tendered%20an%20apology%20only%20to%20release%20himself%20from%20British%20jails%20while%20Punjabis%2C%20who%20were%20hung%20during%20the%20freedom%20struggle%2C%20are%20being%20questioned%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20that%20the%20Punjabis%E2%80%99%20sacrifice%20for%20their%20motherland%20was%20not%20just%20historic%20and%20that%20when%20the%20country%20was%20recently%20humiliated%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20Chinese%20intrusion%20in%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20Galwan%20Valley%2C%20it%20was%20people%20in%20the%20Sikh%20and%20Jat%20regiments%20who%20protected%20India%E2%80%99s%20sovereignty%20and%20gave%20a%20befitting%20reply%20to%20intruders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDallewal%20added%20that%20this%20was%20in%20addition%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Csupreme%20sacrifice%E2%80%9D%20of%20Punjabi%20soldiers%2C%20whom%20he%20called%20sons%20of%20our%20poor%20farmers%20and%20workers%2C%20who%20arrive%20every%20now%20and%20then%20draped%20in%20the%20Indian%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20lecture%20from%20those%20who%20claim%20to%20respect%20the%20national%20flag%20but%20did%20not%20hoist%20it%20in%20their%20Nagpur%20headquarters%20for%20almost%2050%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarwan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20another%20leader%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Chalo%20agitation%2C%20said%20that%20the%20RSS%20is%20now%20thinking%20about%20ending%20the%20concept%20of%20minorities%20and%20accused%20it%20of%20dividing%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandher%20said%20this%20line%20of%20thought%20clearly%20reflected%20the%20RSS%20and%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20polarisation%20agenda%20and%20also%20contradicted%20their%20own%20Citizen%20Amendment%20Act%2C%20which%20promises%20protection%20to%20minorities%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20disruptive%20forces%20like%20the%20RSS%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20good%20for%20the%20country%20and%20its%20constitution%2C%20which%20otherwise%20ensures%20equal%20rights%20to%20all%20citizens%20irrespective%20of%20caste%20and%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20farmer%20leader%2C%20Abhimanyu%20Kohar%2C%20said%20during%20the%20media%20conference%20that%20the%20RSS%20was%20calling%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20farmers%20as%20anarchists%20but%C2%A0%20asked%20what%20was%20to%20be%20made%20of%20farmers%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Haryana%20and%20other%20states%20who%20are%20also%20protesting%20for%20the%20legalisation%20of%20MSPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAre%20they%20anarchists%20too%3F%E2%80%9D%20Kohar%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20whenever%20the%20ruling%20government%20fails%20to%20answer%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20legitimate%20demands%2C%20it%20often%20comes%20out%20with%20all%20sorts%20of%20allegations%20to%20defame%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohar%20continued%20to%20say%20that%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20latest%20allegations%20on%20the%20farmers%20were%20also%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdiversion%20tactics%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20are%20bound%20to%20fail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20why%20senior%20ministers%20from%20the%20BJP%20government%20held%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20negotiations%20with%20protesting%20farmers%20if%20the%20unions%20were%20spreading%20anarchy%20in%20the%20pretext%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYoung%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20death%20takes%20centre%20stage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20death%20of%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%2C%20a%20young%20farmer%20who%20was%20killed%20during%20clashes%20between%20farmers%20and%20security%20forces%20in%20February%2C%20has%20taken%20centre-stage%20in%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20agitation%20against%20the%20BJP-led%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EListing%20out%20the%20agitation%E2%80%99s%20future%20programmes%2C%20Dallewal%20informed%20the%20media%20that%20Shubhkaran%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20mortal%20remains%20are%20being%20carried%20in%20a%20procession%20through%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20remembrance%20of%20him%2C%20a%2