n%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERead%20the%20full%20interview%20here%2C%20which%20has%20been%20edited%20lightly%20for%20language%20and%20brevity.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESravasti%20Dasgupta%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20You%20received%20summons%20from%20the%20CID%20on%20March%2012%20for%20the%20third%20time%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20violations%20and%20property%20damage%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20Assam.%20Did%20you%20go%20to%20the%20CID%20office%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22175208%2Fimage-1779.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22175208%2Fimage-1779.png%20538w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F22175208%2Fimage-1779-300x140.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-694018%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22392%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20meant%20to%20visit%20the%20birthplace%20of%20the%2015th-century%20Vaishnavite%20religious%20leader%2C%20Srimanta%20Shankardev%2C%20stages%20a%20sit-in%20in%20Assam%2C%20on%20January%2022.%20Photo%3A%20X%40INCIndia%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBhupen%20Borah%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20No%2C%20I%20did%20not%20go.%20Yes%2C%20I%20received%20%5Ba%5D%20CID%20notice%20for%20the%20third%20time%2C%20but%20I%20told%20them%20repeatedly%20that%20until%20and%20unless%20I%20complete%20the%20process%20of%20ticket%20distribution%2C%20I%20cannot%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Assam%20Congress%20president%2C%20I%20cannot%20spare%20time%20now.%20You%20can%20arrest%20me%20%5Band%5D%20then%20I%20can%20give%20the%20charge%20to%20one%20of%20the%20senior%20members%20of%20my%20party%2C%20but%20until%20and%20unless%20I%20complete%20the%20ticket%20distribution%20process%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20time%20to%20go%20to%20the%20CID%20office.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20not%20received%20any%20circular%20after%20that.%20I%20have%20only%20announced%2013%20seats%20%5Bfor%20Assam%5D%2C%20one%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20decided.%20After%20that%2C%20if%20they%20call%20me%2C%20I%20will%20definitely%20go.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Why%20do%20you%20think%20the%20Assam%20government%20is%20naming%20you%20in%20this%20case%20of%20property%20damage%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20They%20%5Bthe%20Assam%20police%5D%20have%20registered%20cases%20against%20me%20under%20eight%20sections%2C%20of%20which%20two%20are%20non-bailable%2C%20in%20the%20Jorhat%20police%20station.%20I%20have%20already%20gone%20to%20the%20police%20station%20twice%2C%20where%20they%20have%20interrogated%20me%20for%20over%20six%20to%20seven%20hours.%20During%20the%20Yatra%20I%20was%20attacked%20as%20well.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BThe%20yatra%20used%5D%20The%20same%20venue%20where%20Modi%20addressed%20big%20public%20rallies%20%5Band%5D%20the%20same%20route%20that%20was%20used%20by%20J.P.%20Nadda%20to%20%5Btravel%20to%5D%20Batadrava%2C%20but%20Rahul%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eji%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20stopped.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20protest%20we%20broke%20three%20barricades.%20There%20is%20nothing%20to%20hide%20because%20this%20took%20place%20in%20front%20of%20TV%20cameras.%20As%20%5BCongress%5D%20president%2C%20it%20was%20my%20duty%2C%20since%20my%20leader%20was%20waiting%20to%20go%20to%20Guwahati%20city.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Guwahati%20press%20club%20formally%20invited%20Rahul%20ji%20so%20we%20were%20just%20trying%20to%20go%20there%20to%20meet%20the%20media.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-jodo-nyay-yatra-at-right-time-to-keep-idea-of-india-alive-congress-mp-gaurav-gogoi%5C%22%3EBharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20at%20Right%20Time%2C%20to%20Keep%20Idea%20of%20India%20Alive%3A%20Congress%20MP%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20During%20the%20yatra%2C%20you%20were%20injured%20and%20you%20have%20said%20that%20the%20people%20who%20attacked%20you%20%E2%80%A6%20are%20walking%20free%2C%20while%20you%20are%20being%20summoned.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAre%20you%20saying%20that%20there%20has%20been%20inaction%20by%20the%20state%20government%20and%20targeted%20action%20against%20you%20and%20other%20Congress%20leaders%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20From%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20the%20CM%20first%20tried%20to%20purchase%20me.%20So%20many%20people%20close%20to%20the%20CM%20contacted%20me%20and%20asked%20me%2C%20%E2%80%98What%20%5Bdo%5D%20you%20want%2C%20your%20energy%20will%20be%20wasted%2C%20you%20should%20join%20us%20%5Bthe%20BJP%5D.%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20six%20months%20they%20tried%20and%20when%20they%20found%20that%20I%20am%20committed%20to%20my%20ideology%20and%20my%20party%20leader%2C%20then%20they%20served%20three%20notices%20to%20demolish%20my%20house%20in%20Guwahati.%20But%20due%20to%20civil%20society%20support%2C%20my%20house%20is%20still%20there.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20transferred%20my%20wife%2C%20who%20is%20associate%20professor%20in%20Guwahati%20Medical%20College%2C%20then%20they%20transferred%20my%20brother%20and%20my%20sister-in-law%2C%20and%20lastly%20they%20physically%20attacked%20me%20during%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20have%20also%20reduced%20my%20security.%20So%20first%20they%20tried%20to%20purchase%20me%2C%20but%20now%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20threaten%20me.%20But%20I%20assure%20the%20people%20of%20Assam%20and%20my%20leadership%20that%20I%20will%20not%20compromise.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20recent%20weeks%2C%20we%20have%20seen%20a%20series%20of%20desertions%20by%20Congress%20leaders%20in%20Assam%20before%20elections%2C%20including%20former%20working%20presidents%20Kamalakhya%20Dey%20Purkayastha%2C%20who%20declared%20his%20support%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20and%20Rana%20Goswami%3B%20MLA%20Basanta%20Das%3B%20and%20former%20general%20secretary%20Suruj%20Dehingia%2C%20who%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20the%20Assam%20Congress%20failing%20to%20keep%20its%20flock%20together%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20I%20cannot%20take%20action%20against%20MLAs%2C%20as%20they%20are%20under%20the%20AICC%20%5BAll%20India%20Congress%20Committee%5D%E2%80%99s%20jurisdiction.%20From%20the%20time%20of%20the%20presidential%20elections%20%5Bwhen%20Congress%20MLAs%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fassam-25-mlas-belonging-to-opposition-camp-cross-voted-in-in-favour-of-nda-candidate%2Farticleshow%2F93057411.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecross-voted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20the%20opposition%20candidate%20Yashwant%20Sinha%20in%202022%5D%2C%20we%20know%20Himanta%20Biswa%E2%80%99s%20agents%20are%20within%20us.%20Now%20they%20are%20leaving%20us.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%20said%20before%20also%20that%20we%20want%20a%20Himanta%20Biswa-mukt%20Congress.%20He%20was%20in%20the%20Congress%20for%20so%20many%20years%20%5Band%20so%5D%20he%20has%20maintained%20friendships.%20There%20are%20many%20second-line%20leaders%20who%20will%20come%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F29151333%2FScreenshot-2022-07-29-at-3.13.15-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22910%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F29151333%2FScreenshot-2022-07-29-at-3.13.15-PM.png%20910w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2F29151333%2FScreenshot-2022-07-29-at-3.13.15-PM-300x187.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-610740%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22568%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20Twitter%2F%40himantabiswa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMaybe%20this%20can%20be%20a%20temporary%20setback.%20Because%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20is%20using%20two%20policies%20%E2%80%93%20purchasing%20and%20threatening.%20Now%20he%20is%20indirectly%20threatening%20me.%20Why%20else%20is%20the%20Jorhat%20police%20station%20and%20CID%20calling%20me%20constantly%3F%20That%20means%20they%20are%20threatening%20me%20that%20%E2%80%98either%20you%20surrender%20or%20you%20be%20ready%20for%20punishment%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20a%20mentally%20strong%20person.%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20if%20I%20go%20to%20jail%2C%20but%20some%20people%20care.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESD%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Assam%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20debate%20against%20the%20CAA%20after%20it%20was%20notified%20this%20month.%20The%20AASU%20%5BAll%20Assam%20Students%20Union%5D%20has%20been%20protesting%2C%20Congress%20leaders%20have%20also%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20impact%20will%20the%20CAA%20have%20on%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20your%20assessment%20and%20how%20does%20the%20Congress%20plan%20to%20address%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20is%20a%202019%20law.%20The%20reason%20they%20passed%20the%20notification%20just%20before%20elections%20is%20politically%20motivated.%20We%20have%20decided%20we%20will%20fight%20on%20the%20road%2C%20%5Bon%20the%5D%20court%20and%20in%20ballot%20papers.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20we%20have%20filed%20petitions%20%5Bagainst%5D%20the%20CAA%3B%20secondly%2C%20our%20agitation%20is%20going%20on%20and%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20all%20student%20organisations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%5BA%20forum%20of%5D%20All%2016%20opposition%20parties%20%5Bthe%20United%20Opposition%20Forum%20of%20Assam%5D%20%E2%80%93%20of%20which%20I%20am%20the%20chairman%20%E2%80%93%20%5Bis%5D%20ready%20to%20fight%20against%20the%20CAA.%20But%20as%20elections%20are%20coming%2C%20we%20are%20appealing%20to%20the%20people%20that%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20the%20CAA%2C%20then%20vote%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarbanand%20Sonowal%20%5Bfielded%20by%20the%20BJP%20in%20Dibrugarh%20this%20time%5D%20will%20lose%20because%20he%20was%20CM%20when%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fassam-anti-citizenship-amendment-act-protest-deaths%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efive%20people%20were%20killed%20during%20CAA%20protests%20in%202019%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarma%20has%20also%20said%20that%20Assam%20has%20already%20taken%20a%20lot%20of%20burden%20till%201971%20%5Band%5D%20we%20cannot%20take%20anymore.%20That%20was%20a%20formal%20statement%20given%3B%20now%20only%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20power%2C%20he%20is%20doing%20this%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Assam.