20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19180351%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20An%20analysis%20of%2035%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20which%20purchased%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20details%20of%20which%20the%20SBI%20revealed%20after%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20%E2%80%93%20reveal%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20donated%20are%20members%20of%20two%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20associations%20of%20pharma%20companies%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20March%2018%20had%20refused%20to%20entertain%20petitions%20of%20industry%20bodies%20like%20Assocham%2C%20FICCI%20and%20CII%20on%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20experts%20with%20whom%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20highlighted%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20two%20pharma%20associations%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Indian%20Drugs%20Manufacturers%20Association%20(IDMA)%20and%20the%20Indian%20Pharmaceutical%20Alliance%20(IPA)%20%E2%80%93%20have%20a%20significant%20influence%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20making%2C%20especially%20on%20aspects%20concerning%20drug%20regulation%20and%20drug%20pricing.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETogether%2C%20the%20IDMA%20and%20IPA%20have%20more%20than%201%2C000%20members.%20Both%20these%20associations%20are%20either%20affiliated%20to%20or%20are%20members%20of%20the%20industry%20bodies%20whose%20petitions%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20refused%20to%20hear.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wrote%20to%20both%20the%20associations%20on%20March%2018%20seeking%20their%20reaction%20to%20these%20political%20donations.%20Their%20replies%20will%20be%20added%20if%20and%20when%20they%20come.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20present%20analysis%20includes%20only%20drug%20makers%20and%20excludes%20hospital(s)%20figuring%20in%20the%20list%20of%20electoral%20bond%20donors.%20For%20the%20sake%20of%20uniformity%2C%20this%20list%20also%20excludes%20companies%20which%20make%20medical%20equipment%20and%20those%20which%20make%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eonly%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20vaccines.%20For%20instance%2C%20Bharat%20Biotech%2C%20according%20to%20the%20SBI%20database%2C%20donated%20Rs%2010%20crore%20in%20electoral%20bonds%20%E2%80%93%20but%20has%20been%20excluded%20from%20the%20current%20analysis.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20analysis%2C%20therefore%2C%20covers%20almost%20all%20drug%20makers%20who%20donated%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20according%20to%20the%20SBI%20database.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20finds%20that%20out%20of%20the%20top%20five%20pharma%20donors%2C%20four%20are%20either%20members%20of%20the%20IDPA%2C%20the%20IPA%20or%20both.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDr%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20Laboratories%2C%20which%20bought%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2080%20crores%2C%20is%20the%20top%20purchaser%20in%20this%20category.%20It%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20IDMA%20and%20the%20IPA.%20Similarly%2C%20Natco%20Pharma%20Limited%20(which%20spent%20Rs%2069.25%20crores)%20is%20a%20member%20of%20both%20the%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETorrent%20Pharmaceuticals%20(Rs%2077.5%20crore)%20and%20the%20Hetero%20group%20(Rs%2060%20crore)%20are%20the%20part%20of%20the%20IDMA%2C%20while%20one%20among%20the%20top%20five%20purchasers%2C%20Divis%20Laboratories%20Limited%20(Rs%2055%20crore)%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20any%20of%20the%20two%20groups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20detailed%20analysis%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20bonds%20bought%20by%20the%2035%20pharmaceutical%20companies%2C%20and%20their%20membership%20of%20both%20or%20either%20of%20the%20two%20bodies%20is%20presented%20below%20in%20this%20three-page%20list.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F17215966%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F17215966%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F17215966%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIncidentally%20the%20total%20of%20Rs%20799.66%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20donated%20by%20these%2035%20drugmakers%2C%20is%20more%20than%20half%20of%20what%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20allocated%20in%20the%20Union%20Budget%202024-25%20under%20the%20head%20%E2%80%98development%20of%20pharmaceutical%20industry%E2%80%99.%20This%20money%20was%20to%20be%20utilised%20by%20the%20department%20of%20pharmaceuticals%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20this%20head%2C%20the%20government%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20builds%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpharmaceuticals.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2FGuidelines%2520of%2520the%2520Scheme%2520Promotion%2520of%2520Bulk%2520Drug%2520Parks_1.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebulk%20drug%20parks%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eto%20%E2%80%9Csignificantly%20bring%20down%20the%20manufacturing%20cost%20of%20the%20bulk%20drugs.%E2%80%9D%20This%20is%2C%20thus%2C%20understood%20to%20be%20hand%20holding%20by%20the%20government%20so%20that%20the%20pharma%20industry%20grows.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%2C%20however%2C%20it%20turns%20out%20that%20the%20pharma%20industry%20is%20investing%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20their%20profits%20as%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20the%20experts%20who%20spoke%20with%20The%20Wire%20noted%20that%20it%20was%20a%20revelation%20to%20see%20the%20financial%20connections%20between%20the%20government%20and%20pharma%20connections%20set%20out%20so%20clearly%20in%20the%20form%20of%20electoral%20bond%20data.%20It%20had%20been%20conjecture%20until%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20various%20developments%2C%20over%20a%20period%20of%20time%2C%20including%20in%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20makes%20one%20wonder%20if%20pharma%20companies%20and%20their%20associations%20are%20being%20treated%20with%20kid%20gloves.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDoc-pharma%20guidelines%20still%20not%20mandatory%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20sets%20of%20guidelines%20that%20were%20put%20out%20by%20the%20government%20was%20a%20code%20regulating%20the%20relationship%20between%20doctors%20and%20pharmaceutical%20companies.%20Known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98Uniform%20Code%20of%20Pharmaceutical%20Marketing%20Practices%E2%80%99%20(UCPMP)%2C%C2%A0%20it%20stipulates%20a%20number%20of%20important%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20says%20the%20pharma%20firms%20must%20not%20organise%20leisure%20travel%20trips%20for%20doctors%2C%20should%20not%20hold%20medical%20conferences%20in%20foreign%20countries%2C%20and%20should%20not%20offer%20any%20gift%20to%20healthcare%20professionals%2C%20among%20other%20things.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20idea%20of%20the%20UCPMP%20is%20to%20stop%20unethical%20practices%20that%20pharma%20companies%20may%20adopt%20to%20lure%20doctors%20in%20exchange%20for%20prescribing%20drugs%20sold%20by%20the%20company.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20here%20that%20pharma%20associations%20like%20the%20IDMA%2C%20the%20IPA%20and%20others%20are%20ones%20that%20are%20supposed%20to%20adjudicate%20whether%20a%20pharma%20company%20has%20violated%20the%20UCPMP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UCPMP%2C%20if%20a%20complaint%20is%20received%20against%20any%20of%20their%20members%20violating%20it%2C%20these%20associations%20can%20take%20a%20final%20call%20on%20that.%20They%20can%20expel%20it%20from%20the%20association%20concerned%20%E2%80%93%20the%20punishment%20described%20in%20the%20UCPMP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20problem%20with%20the%20implementation%20of%20UCPMP%20was%20that%20it%20was%20voluntary.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fnew-code-for-doctor-pharma-unethical-practices-notified-but-remains-non-mandatory%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20detailed%20piece%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20reported%20how%2C%20though%20the%20government%20did%20away%20with%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98voluntary%E2%80%99%20from%20the%C2%A0%20UCPMP%2C%C2%A0%20which%20was%20there%20in%20its%20previous%20version%2C%20it%20stopped%20short%20of%20making%20it%20mandatory%20%E2%80%93%20a%20long-pending%20demand%20of%20health%20activists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20story%20was%20published%20on%20March%2013%2C%202024%2C%20a%20government%20spokesperson%20texted%20this%20reporter%20to%20say%20the%20UCPMP%20is%20not%20voluntary%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20message%20read%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%5BThe%5DUCPMP%20is%20not%20voluntary%20anymore.%20It%20is%20mandatory.%20The%20entire%20process%20will%20be%20under%20Government%20oversight.%20Read%20section%2012%20(v)%20of%20the%20Code.%20Any%C2%A0%20Government%20agency%20or%20authority%20can%20be%20brought%20in%20as%20per%20statutes%20and%20as%20relevant%20to%20the%20context.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20media%20outlets%20also%20reported%20that%20the%20code%20has%20become%20mandatory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13005018%2FShastri-Bhavan-1024x512.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13005018%2FShastri-Bhavan-1024x512.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13005018%2FShastri-Bhavan-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13005018%2FShastri-Bhavan-800x400.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13005018%2FShastri-Bhavan.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701394%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22420%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EShastri%20Bhawan.%20Photo%3A%20Pinakpani%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20CC%20BY-SA%204.0.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20posed%20two%20follow-up%20questions%20to%20the%20government%20spokesperson%2C%20which%20till%20date%20remain%20unanswered.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20%E2%80%9Cstatues%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9Coversight%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccontexts%E2%80%9D%20are%20being%20referred%20to%20here%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20importantly%2C%20if%20the%20code%20is%20mandatory%2C%20where%20is%20the%20force%20of%20law%20to%20support%20it%3B%20and%20could%20the%20spokesperson%20point%20to%20a%20relevant%20gazetted%20notification%20to%20say%20which%20law%20of%20the%20land%20governs%20the%20code%20if%20the%20government%20were%20to%20take%20any%20action%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20section%2012%20(v)%20of%20the%20Code%2C%20which%20the%20spokesperson%20referred%20to%2C%20it%20states%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cases%20where%20disciplinary%2C%20penal%2C%20or%20remedial%20action%20lies%20within%20the%20domain%20of%20any%20agency%20or%20authority%20of%20the%20Government%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20statute%2C%20the%20%5BEthics%5D%20Committee%20%5Bof%20pharmaceutical%20associations%5D%20may%20send%20its%20recommendations%20to%20such%20agency%20or%20authority%20through%20the%20Department%20of%20Pharmaceuticals.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENow%20if%20at%20all%20an%20ethics%20committee%20of%20the%20pharma%20associations%20does%20decide%20to%20refer%20the%20matter%20to%20the%20government%2C%20what%20penalty%20the%20government%20can%20impose%20is%20not%20clear.%20Neither%20does%20the%20code%20say%20anything%20nor%20is%20it%20clear%20which%20law%20the%20government%20would%20use%20to%20punish%20the%20erring%20firms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20version%20of%20the%20UCPMP%2C%20which%20replaced%20the%2010-year-old%20version%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20scope%20of%20%3Cem%3Esuo%20motu%3C%2Fem%3E%20action%20against%20the%20erring%20firms.%20Someone%20has%20to%20collect%20evidence%20against%20a%20firm%20to%20establish%20the%20violation.%20Also%2C%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20complainant%20has%20to%20be%20mandatorily%20revealed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20tilts%20the%20equation%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20companies%20and%20makes%20the%20job%20of%20the%20complainants%20difficult%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr%20Gurinder%20S.%20Grewal%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Association%20of%20Doctors%20for%20Ethical%20Healthcare%20(ADEH).%20The%20ADEH%20also%20issued%20a%20statement%20on%20March%2018%20berating%20the%20government%20for%20not%20coming%20out%20with%20a%20mandatory%20code.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDrug%20pricing%20rule%20committee%20has%20pharma%20associations%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20March%2012%2C%202024%2C%20the%20government%20issued%20a%20notification%20for%20the%20constitution%20of%20a%20committee%20for%20%E2%80%98reforms%20in%20the%20pricing%20framework%20for%20drugs%20and%20medical%20devices%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20committee%20is%20supposed%20to%20revise%20the%20Drug%20Pricing%20Control%20Order%20(DPCO)%20of%202013.%20The%20DPCO-2013%20fixed%20the%20prices%20of%20about%20300-odd%20drugs%20which%20the%20government%20felt%20constituted%20an%20%E2%80%98essential%20list%20of%20medicines%E2%80%99.%20Now%2C%20the%20committee%20is%20tasked%20with%20the%20revision%20of%20the%20DPCO.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20apart%20from%20the%20three%20government%20officials%2C%20the%20committee%20comprises%20two%20%E2%80%98special%20invitees%E2%80%99%20as%20well.%20They%20are%20representatives%20of%20the%20two%20pharma%20associations%20discussed%20above%20%E2%80%93%20the%20IDMA%20and%20the%20IPA.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20departure%20from%20%5Bthe%5D%20usual%20process%2C%20the%20IDMA%20and%20the%20IPA%C2%A0%20have%20been%20granted%20privileged%20access%20as%20special%20invitees%20to%20the%20committee%2C%20rather%20than%20maintaining%20a%20neutral%20stand%20and%20treating%20all%20stakeholders%20%5Bincluding%20civil%20society%20groups%20advocating%20for%20affordable%20drugs%5D%20at%20par%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Malini%20Aisola%2C%20co-convenor%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Drug%20Action%20Network%20(AIDAN).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20earlier%20occasions%2C%20both%20the%20industry%20representatives%20and%20the%20civil%20society%20groups%20would%20be%20called%20for%20consultations%20as%20independent%20stakeholders%20but%20none%20would%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20committee%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20change%2C%20a%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20individuals%20advocating%20for%20affordable%20drugs%20allege%2C%20is%20a%20conflict%20of%20interest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DPCO%20applies%20to%20the%20medicines%20which%20fall%20under%20the%20essential%20list.%20For%20the%20majority%20of%20drugs%20falling%20outside%20this%20list%2C%20there%20is%20no%20cap%20on%20prices.%20Attempts%20by%20the%20government%20to%20impose%20any%20cap%20under%20%E2%80%98trade%20margin%20rationalisation%E2%80%99%20plan%20have%20fallen%20flat%20due%20to%20opposition%20by%20some%20pharma%20associations.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENMC%E2%80%99s%20stringent%20ethics%20also%20dropped%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20(NMC)%2C%20which%20regulates%20practising%20doctors%2C%20replaced%20its%20own%20code%20of%20ethics%20with%20a%20new%20one%20last%20year.%20Among%20other%20things%2C%20it%20sought%20to%20ban%20pharma-sponsored%20medical%20conferences.%20However%2C%20within%20days%20of%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20new%20code%2C%20the%20government%20put%20it%20in%20abeyance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20health%20ministry%20opposed%20the%20NMC%20regulations%20after%20one-sided%20discussions%20with%20some%20groups%2C%20including%20IPA%20and%20Organisation%20of%20Pharmaceuticals%20Producers%20of%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20claimed%20Aisola%2C%20as%20she%20said%2C%20she%20had%20been%20tracking%20what%20led%20to%20the%20decision%20of%20abandonment%20of%20the%20new%20ethics.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20health%20ministry%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20negative%20impact%20on%20big%20manufacturers%20propagating%20prominent%20brands%2C%20while%20also%20backing%20sponsorship%20by%20pharma%20companies%20of%20the%20medical%20conferences%C2%A0%20of%20doctors%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20medical%20practice%20would%20deteriorate%20if%20sponsorships%20were%20disallowed%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20only%20had%20the%20Indian%20Medical%20Association%20(IMA)%20opposed%20the%20new%20ethics%2C%20even%20some%20of%20the%20pharma%20associations%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20COVID-19%20question%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20during%20the%20challenging%20times%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20many%20had%20said%20that%20the%20government%20had%20done%20less%20than%20what%20was%20desirable%20to%20regulate%20the%20pharma%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20emergency-use%20authorisations%20for%20some%20COVID%20drugs%20were%20granted%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20problematic%20data.%20For%20instance%2C%20Glenmark%E2%80%99s%20Favipiravir%20failed%20to%20show%20any%20benefit%20in%20its%20trial.%20Similarly%2C%20Itolizumab%20was%20surprisingly%20exempted%20from%20conducting%20a%20Phase%203%20trial%20even%20while%20concerns%20about%20incomplete%20disclosure%20of%20Phase%202%20results%20remained%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Siddhartha%20Das%2C%20another%20member%20of%20the%20AIDAN.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20authorisations%20were%20never%20revoked%20even%20when%20problems%20came%20to%20light%20and%20the%20companies%20involved%20went%20on%20to%20make%20massive%20profits%20during%20the%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20issue%20he%20pointed%20out%20was%20the%20escalated%20prices%20of%20drugs%20during%20COVID-19.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20spite%20of%20the%20requests%20for%20governmental%20intervention%20to%20lower%20prices%20of%20COVID%20related%20medications%20and%20massive%20price%20hikes%20adding%20to%20the%20distress%20of%20patients%2C%20the%20National%20Pharmaceutical%20Pricing%20Authority%20failed%20to%20act%20except%20to%20request%20compliance%20of%20companies%20selling%20Remdesvir%20to%20voluntarily%20reduce%20their%20price.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20for%20funding%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20ADEH%E2%80%99s%20Grewal%20said%2C%20if%20the%20pharma%20firms%20could%20donate%20to%20political%20parties%2C%20then%20they%20must%20not%20resist%20the%20margin%20(profit)%20rationalisation%20plans%2C%20which%20would%20significantly%20reduce%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20drugs%20and%2C%20therefore%2C%20the%20out-of-pocket%20expenditure%20of%20the%20common%20people%20also.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710852061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19180351%2FUntitled-design-12.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fpharma-company-electoral-bonds-policy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Many%20firms%20belong%20to%20two%20pharma%20associations%20which%20have%20a%20significant%20influence%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20policy%20making.%20The%20amount%20they%20have%20donated%20is%20more%20than%20half%20of%20what%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20set%20in%20its%20Budget%20to%20grow%20the%20pharma%20industry.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fpharma-company-electoral-bonds-policy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22JNU%20Teachers'%20Association%20Condemns%20Right-Wing%20Disruption%20of%20Nivedita%20Menon%20Talk%20in%20Odisha%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F17141400%2F00056.01_43_00_05.Still006.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University%20Teachers%E2%80%99%20Association%20(JNUTA)%20has%20issued%20a%20statement%20in%20support%20of%20varsity%20professor%20Nivedita%20Menon%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20forced%20to%20leave%20the%20podium%20during%20a%20talk%20at%20the%20Gangadhar%20Meher%20University%20in%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20Sambalpur%20due%20to%20disruptions%20by%20a%20right-wing%20Hindu%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20her%20talk%20at%20GMU%20titled%20%E2%80%98Feminisms%20for%20the%2021st%20century%E2%80%99%20was%20disrupted%20after%20she%20had%20spoken%20for%20about%2015%20minutes%20of%20her%20inaugural%20talk%20by%20a%20handful%20of%20people%E2%80%94mostly%20outsiders%20to%20GMU%E2%80%94who%20shouted%20slogans%20to%20intimidate%20Menon%20and%20prevented%20her%20from%20speaking%2C%20her%20online%20talk%20at%20Sambalpur%20University%20was%20not%20allowed%20to%20be%20streamed%2C%E2%80%9D%20JNUTA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20disruption%20and%20intimidation%20of%20Menon%20by%20anti-academic%20elements%20is%20a%20grave%20assault%20on%20academic%20freedom%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20continued%2C%20adding%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20extremely%20worrying%20that%20attendees%20were%20forced%20to%20leave%2C%20depriving%20them%20of%20the%20opportunity%20for%20dialogue%20and%20exchange%20of%20ideas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20493px)%2085vw%2C%20493px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19152510%2F432647446_7262737703816552_2553822880526045087_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22493%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19152510%2F432647446_7262737703816552_2553822880526045087_n.jpeg%20686w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F19152510%2F432647446_7262737703816552_2553822880526045087_n-214x300.jpeg%20214w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-702364%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22690%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Fodisha%2F2024%2FMar%2F13%2Fjnu-professor-forced-to-leave-podium-amid-protests-at-gmu%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20students%20allegedly%20belonging%20to%20the%20Akhil%20Bharatiya%20Vidyarthi%20Parishad%20disrupted%20Menon%E2%80%99s%20March%2