0Mahapatra%20(left)%20and%20police%20officer%20Bhaskar%20Jadhav.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1710338115.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1710338115-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1710338115-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1710338115-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1710338115-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344785%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ELawyer%20Supriyo%20Ranjan%20Mahapatra%20(left)%20and%20police%20officer%20Bhaskar%20Jadhav.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Bhaskar%20Jadhav%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F236534%2Fmumbai-consumer-rights-court-case-how-to-mrp-over-extra-overcharging-fine-police-ice-cream-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBhaskar%20Jadhav%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20from%20the%20Mumbai%20Police%2C%20was%20charged%20Rs%2010%20more%20than%20the%20MRP%20of%20an%20ice%20cream%20pack%20under%20%E2%80%98cooling%20charges%E2%80%99.%20On%20asking%20they%20justified%20the%20billing%20cost%20by%20stating%20the%20electricity%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wondered%20if%20they%20could%20fool%20a%20policeman%2C%20they%20must%20be%20doing%20it%20with%20so%20many%20of%20their%20innocent%20customers.%20I%20wanted%20to%20uphold%20the%20law%2C%20and%20so%20I%20filed%20the%20case%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20saved%20the%20bill%20containing%20the%20GST%20number%20along%20with%20the%20ice%20cream%20packet%20as%20evidence.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20under%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%2C%202019%20%E2%80%94%20which%20allows%20consumers%20to%20file%20complaints%20with%20the%20Consumer%20Disputes%20Redressal%20Commissions%20(CDRCs)%20if%20they%20are%20being%20charged%20more%20than%20the%20MRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20the%20District%20Commissioner%20Disputes%20Redressal%20Forum%20directed%20Mumbai-based%20Shagun%20Veg%20Restaurant%20to%20pay%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%2C%20pay%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Bhaskar%20as%20compensation%20for%20%E2%80%98mental%20torture%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20refund%20the%20extra%20charge%20of%20Rs%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Rohit%20Patel%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20was%20charged%20Rs%20164%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F246864%2Fhow-to-consumer-rights-court-case-ahmedabad-mrp-over-extra-overcharging-bottled-water-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebottle%20of%20water%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20was%20actually%20priced%20at%20Rs%2020.%20He%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20the%20hotel%20at%20the%20Ahmedabad%20(Rural)%20Consumer%20Disputes%20Redressal%20under%20the%20Consumer%20Protection%20Act%2C%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20charged%20150%2B%20taxes.%20When%20I%20asked%20the%20manager%2C%20he%20said%20the%20additional%20charge%20was%20a%20service%20charge%20and%20service%20tax.%20I%20found%20their%20arguments%20ridiculous%20so%20I%20warned%20them%20about%20going%20to%20the%20Consumer%20Forum%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20he%20went%20to%20the%20forum%2C%20made%20an%20affidavit%2C%20filled%20out%20a%20complaint%20form%2C%20and%20kept%20his%20evidence%20%E2%80%94%20the%20bottle%20and%20the%20hotel%20bill%2C%20ready.%20Once%20his%20complaint%20was%20approved%2C%20a%20legal%20notice%20was%20sent%20to%20the%20hotel%20and%20the%20proceedings%20required%20Rohit%20to%20appear%20in%20court%2028%20times!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Rohit%20did%20not%20give%20up%2C%20and%20after%20a%20five-year-long%20legal%20battle%2C%20the%20hotel%20was%20asked%20to%20refund%20the%20overpriced%20amount%20and%20pay%20Rs%202%2C500%20for%20harassment%20charges%20and%20Rs%203%2C000%20for%20other%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vijay%20Gopal%20(left)%20and%20Rohit%20Patel.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fconsumer-rights-1-1710338189-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-344786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EVijay%20Gopal%20(left)%20and%20Rohit%20Patel.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Vijay%20Gopal%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20Hyderabad%E2%80%99s%20Vijay%20had%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20BookMyShow%20and%20the%20multiplex%20chain%20PVR%20for%20charging%20Rs%2080.12%20extra%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F180422%2Fpaytm-movie-tickets-internet-handling-fees-rbi-vijay-gopal-ind