ity.%20However%2C%20the%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20to%20Rs%203%20lakh%20to%20install%20a%20rooftop%20solar%20system%20is%20often%20difficult%20for%20most%20middle-class%20families%20in%20Indian%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20this%20consultation%2C%20we%20also%20take%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20PAN%20card%2C%20check%20his%20loan%20EMI%20eligibility%2C%20and%20present%20the%20EMI%20schemes%20we%20can%20offer%20to%20them.%20People%20can%20go%20solar%20on%20a%20six-month%20zero-cost%20EMI%2C%2012-month%20EMI%2C%20or%2060-month%20EMI.%20That%20makes%20it%20an%20affordable%20proposition.%20Also%2C%20in%20case%20of%2060-month%20EMI%2C%20their%20initial%20down%20payment%20to%20us%20gets%20covered%20through%20the%20subsidy%20given%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Shreya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20power%20a%202%20to%203-BHK%20home%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247226%2Fbengaluru-startup-clairco-innovation-air-pollution-turn-ac-into-air-filter-aayush-jha-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20conditioners%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20consumer%20will%20need%20a%203-kW%20to%204-kW%20solar%20installation.%20If%20such%20homes%20have%20an%20air%20conditioner%2C%20they%20may%20require%205-kW%20to%206-kW.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20commonly%20sold%20residential%20rooftop%20solar%20installation%20is%203-kW.%20A%20solar%20kit%20for%20this%20energy%20requirement%20is%20about%20Rs%202%20lakh%2C%20of%20which%20the%20Government%20covers%20Rs%2078%2C000%20as%20a%20subsidy%20(under%20the%20latest%20%E2%80%98PM-Surya%20Ghar%3A%20Muft%20Bijli%20Yojana%E2%80%99).%20The%20consumer%20ends%20up%20paying%20only%20about%20Rs%201.2%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22w